Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:12.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,片名：這個殺手不太冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:02.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Allora, come stai, Leone?\N{\rCHT}最近怎麼樣 里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:05.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bene.\N{\rCHT}挺好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:12.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.Let's talk business.\N{\rCHT}好吧 我們來談點正經事兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:15.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,This fat bastard is moving in\N{\rCHT}這個死胖子插手了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:16.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,on Morizio's business.\N{\rCHT}莫里奇奧的買賣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:20.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know Morizio is a reasonable guy.\N{\rCHT}你知道莫里奇奧是講道理的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:23.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,He just wants a little conversation.\N{\rCHT}他只想談談{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:26.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,But this guy, he don't wanna hear about it.\N{\rCHT}但這傢伙 他不想聽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll listen to you.\N{\rCHT}或許他會聽你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:30.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,He comes to town every Tuesday.\N{\rCHT}他每週二來鎮上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:32.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you free Tuesday?\N{\rCHT}你週二有空嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:37.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm free Tuesday.\N{\rCHT}嗯 有空{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:55.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you again, Mr. Jones.\N{\rCHT}真高興再見到你 鐘斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:12.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Remember, neatness counts.You got one half hour.\N{\rCHT}記住 辦得俐落點 給你半小時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,One hour.\N{\rCHT}一小時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:36.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yea... What?\N{\rCHT}怎麼了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's Tonto, downstairs.\N{\rCHT}我是樓下的唐托{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's a guy wants to talk to you.\N{\rCHT}這兒有個人想跟你談談{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:45.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's he look like?\N{\rCHT}他長什麼樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:48.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Serious.\N{\rCHT}蠻嚴肅的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:50.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tell him I'm coming up.\N{\rCHT}告訴他我要上來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's coming up.\N{\rCHT}他要上來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:59.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Somebody's coming up. Somebody serious.\N{\rCHT}有人來了 來者不善{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:04.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mickey,\N{\rCHT}米基{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,open your eyes. We got company.\N{\rCHT}眼睛擦亮點 有人來砸場兒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,We got company.\N{\rCHT}有人來砸場兒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on.\N{\rCHT}來吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:35.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop, man!\N{\rCHT}住手 快住手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tonto.\N{\rCHT}唐托{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:48.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tell the driver to wait for us out back, and hurry up.\N{\rCHT}叫在外面等我們的司機回來 趕緊的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:37.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey sweetie, what's going on?\N{\rCHT}親愛噠 腫麼啦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:41.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, baby.It's cool. Take a nap.\N{\rCHT}寶貝 別擔心 沒事兒 你再歇會兒吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.\N{\rCHT}天哪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Those fuckers blocked both the exits.\N{\rCHT}這些混蛋把兩個出口都堵了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:09.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Check the terrace!\N{\rCHT}去檢查陽臺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,911 emergency.\N{\rCHT}這裡是911緊急熱線{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,I need help. Somebody's trying to kill me.\N{\rCHT}救命 有人要殺我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:29.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Alright. Just stay on the line. I'll just be off a moment.\N{\rCHT}請別掛機 馬上幫您轉接{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sir, I'm gonna connect you with an officer.\N{\rCHT}先生 即將為您接通一個警官{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Detective Jefferson. May I help you?\N{\rCHT}我是傑弗遜警探 有什麼需要幫助的嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:56.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll call you back.\N{\rCHT}待會兒再打給你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Relax, man.\N{\rCHT}兄弟 放鬆點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:05.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got half of Bolivia sitting in them suitcases.\N{\rCHT}那邊手提箱裡的毒品可以買下半個玻利維亞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:06.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hasn't even been cut yet.\N{\rCHT}還沒勾兌過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:08.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, take it.It's yours.\N{\rCHT}去吧 拿走吧 都歸你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dial this number.\N{\rCHT}撥這個號碼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:31.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to you later, sweetie, okay?\N{\rCHT}親愛的 我們回頭再約哈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bye.\N{\rCHT}拜拜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:39.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello?\N{\rCHT}你好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's Morizio. Remember me?\N{\rCHT}我是莫里奇奧 還記得我嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:43.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,I see you're back in town.\N{\rCHT}我知道你回鎮上了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:47.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I mean, no.Just for today.\N{\rCHT}嗯 哦不 我的意思是 就待今天一天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:51.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,So it's safe to say today's your last day in town...\N{\rCHT}那不妨說今天也是你在鎮上的最後一天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,and we'll never see your fat fucking face again.\N{\rCHT}我們再也不用看到你那張肥豬臉了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Right.\N{\rCHT}對對對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let me speak to our mutual friend.\N{\rCHT}讓我跟咱們共同的朋友說兩句{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:02.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,He wants to talk to you.\N{\rCHT}他要你接電話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:08.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}嗯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:12.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Make sure he understands, and let him go.\N{\rCHT}確保他明白我的意思 然後讓他滾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?\N{\rCHT}你明白了嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,So say it.\N{\rCHT}說出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,I understand.\N{\rCHT}我明白了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:30.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good.\N{\rCHT}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:58.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus.\N{\rCHT}蒼天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:11.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Two milk as usual?\N{\rCHT}照例兩盒牛奶嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:17.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hi\N{\rCHT}嗨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why did you hide the cigarette?\N{\rCHT}你為什麼把煙藏起來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,This building's full of rats.\N{\rCHT}樓裡到處是耗子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:29.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,I didn't want my old man to find out.\N{\rCHT}我可不想我家老頭兒發現{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Got enough problems.\N{\rCHT}麻煩夠多了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,What happened?\N{\rCHT}怎麼弄的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:44.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,I fell off my bike.\N{\rCHT}騎自行車摔的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:02.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't tell my dad about the cigarette, okay?\N{\rCHT}不要告訴我爸香煙的事兒 好嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Why are you doing this to us? - I don't know...\N{\rCHT}- 你為什麼這麼對我們 - 我真的不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,People got memory problems these days.\N{\rCHT}現在人都很健忘的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:19.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,It must be the sun.\N{\rCHT}一定是太陽把腦子燒壞了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Know when to come out of the sun.\N{\rCHT}少曬點太陽 好好想想{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:23.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know how it happened.\N{\rCHT}我不知道怎麼會發生這種事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's my job? I'm just a holder.\N{\rCHT}我只負責保管{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,I hold the stuff you give to me.\N{\rCHT}保管你們給我的東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't look at it or touch it.\N{\rCHT}不看 不碰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to cut it.\N{\rCHT}我甚至不知道怎麼稀釋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Try to follow me.\N{\rCHT}聽著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:31.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,In June, we gave you the dope.\N{\rCHT}我們六月份給你這些毒品{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:32.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,It tests 100 percent pure.\N{\rCHT}當時純度還是百分之百{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now it's July, we pick up the dope,\N{\rCHT}現在七月了 我們再來拿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:36.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,and it tests 90 percent pure.\N{\rCHT}測出來純度只有百分之九十{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Somewhere between June and July,\N{\rCHT}六月到七月中的某個時間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,ten percent turned to cut!\N{\rCHT}百分之十的純度不見了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:41.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know. It's none of my business.\N{\rCHT}我不知道 不關我的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:43.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,You give me the stuff, I hold it.\N{\rCHT}你給了我 我就只負責保管{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's all I know.\N{\rCHT}我就知道這麼多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:46.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look, you know, I'm trying to help you out here...\N{\rCHT}好吧 你看 我在試圖拉你出苦海{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:49.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,but if you're gonna be a hard-ass about it...\N{\rCHT}但你要是再這麼嘴硬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,I gotta disturb him.\N{\rCHT}我就要去打擾他了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you.\N{\rCHT}告訴你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,When he's into his music,\N{\rCHT}他沉浸在音樂中的時候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,he hates being disturbed.\N{\rCHT}最恨被人打擾了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you the truth.\N{\rCHT}我說的都是實話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:00.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,I hope so,\N{\rCHT}但願如此{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:03.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,because he's got a talent for sniffin' out a lie.\N{\rCHT}因為他有嗅出謊言的天賦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:08.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's scary.It's almost like a sixth sense.\N{\rCHT}很嚇人的 就像是第六感{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:10.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna\N{\rCHT}你是要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:11.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,change your tune\N{\rCHT}改變主意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:12.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,or I gotta bust into his?\N{\rCHT}還是要我去麻煩他呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:17.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you the truth.\N{\rCHT}我說的就是實話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right.\N{\rCHT}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:29.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stan.\N{\rCHT}史丹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:30.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stan.\N{\rCHT}史丹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:37.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. He said he didn't cut the dope.\N{\rCHT}對不起 他說他沒稀釋毒品{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:41.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh\N{\rCHT}哦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Of course he didn't.\N{\rCHT}他當然沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:35.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just do me a favor.Find out who did by tomorrow.\N{\rCHT}幫我個忙 明天查出來是誰做的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:36.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Noon.\N{\rCHT}正午之前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:50.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Malky, wait.\N{\rCHT}瑪律奇 等等{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:55.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,I didn't cut your shit.Find out yourself!\N{\rCHT}我又沒做 你自己查去吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:01.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you doin' out here?\N{\rCHT}你在這兒幹嘛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:03.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get inside and do your homework.\N{\rCHT}進去做你的作業{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,I did it already.\N{\rCHT}我做完了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? Get inside and help your sister\N{\rCHT}是嗎 那滾進去幫你姐姐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,clean up the goddamn house!\N{\rCHT}打掃下該死的屋子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,And stop smoking cigarettes!\N{\rCHT}不許再抽煙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:10.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Time's up. My turn.\N{\rCHT}時間到了 該我看了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:14.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Change the channel, and I'll smash your face.\N{\rCHT}你要是敢換台 我就撕碎你的臉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:28.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sweetheart.\N{\rCHT}抱歉 親愛的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh Sweetie\N{\rCHT}早 小寶貝兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:37.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hi, honey, you two.\N{\rCHT}嗨 親愛的 好孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sweetheart, turn that down.\N{\rCHT}寶貝 把聲音調低點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mama's got a headache.\N{\rCHT}媽媽頭疼死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:43.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,She took my turn.\N{\rCHT}她占了我的時間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:45.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,She wants to watch goddamn cartoons!\N{\rCHT}她要看傻X的動畫片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:47.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't hurt her to move her ass.\N{\rCHT}運動下她屁股又不會死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:49.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one with a fat ass around here.\N{\rCHT}我又不是屁股肥的那一個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can someone who's doing nothing all day\N{\rCHT}那個整天除了看動畫片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,but watching cartoons...\N{\rCHT}屁事不做的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,move a little ass and go get some food?\N{\rCHT}能動下她的小屁屁去弄點吃的嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I dare you to say that again.\N{\rCHT}有本事再說一遍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:08.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Margie, I think I screwed up.\N{\rCHT}瑪姬 我好像搞砸了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be the first time.\N{\rCHT}反正也不是第一次了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,You always come up with somethin', right?\N{\rCHT}你總是惹出些麻煩事兒 是吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think I went too far this time.\N{\rCHT}我覺得這次越線了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're goin' too far right now.\N{\rCHT}你現在才叫越線{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be late for work.\N{\rCHT}我上班要遲到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:20.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,How about workin' at home today?\N{\rCHT}不如今天在家工作吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:31.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn!\N{\rCHT}[動畫]現在輪到我了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:34.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit! She's gonna hit me! Daddy!\N{\rCHT}該死 她要打我 爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:37.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit! Shut the goddamn door!\N{\rCHT}草 把門關上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:42.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fuckin' bitch.\N{\rCHT}小賤人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can somebody answer the phone?\N{\rCHT}誰接下電話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:55.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm busy!\N{\rCHT}我忙著呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:03.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello?\N{\rCHT}喂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:05.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is Marguerite McCallister...\N{\rCHT}我是瑪格麗特·麥卡利斯特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:08.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,headmistress at the Spencer School in Wildwood, NewJersey.\N{\rCHT}新澤西 威爾伍德市 斯賓瑟學校的校長{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is Mr. Or Mrs. Lando home?\N{\rCHT}蘭多先生或女士在家嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is she.\N{\rCHT}在 我就是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:20.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Lando, when your husband enrolled Mathilda at Spencer...\N{\rCHT}蘭多女士 當您丈夫在斯賓瑟為瑪蒂爾達註冊時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:22.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,he told us she had "Problems."\N{\rCHT}他告訴我們她有點"問題"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,As you know, we pride ourselves on\N{\rCHT}正如您所知 我們致力於{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:27.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,turning troubled girls into healthy, productive young women.\N{\rCHT}將問題少女們培養成健康 有成就的年輕女性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:30.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,But if they are not here, there is very little we can do.\N{\rCHT}但是如果她們人都不在這 我們能做的就非常少了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:33.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mathilda left school without permission nearly two weeks ago.\N{\rCHT}大約兩個星期前 瑪蒂爾達未經允許離開了學校{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:37.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know your husband paid tuition in advance for a year...\N{\rCHT}我知道您的丈夫預付了一年學費{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:39.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,but if you will refer to the page 20\N{\rCHT}但是如果您去查閱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:41.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,in the rules and regulations manual we sent you...\N{\rCHT}我們寄給您的學生守則第20頁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:44.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,you will see that unless there is a valid excuse\N{\rCHT}您就會發現 長期缺席者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:47.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,for prolonged absence your tuition will be forfeit.\N{\rCHT}除非有正當理由 學費將不會退回{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's dead.\N{\rCHT}她死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:14.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tell that fuckin' kid to do a little work around here!\N{\rCHT}叫那混蛋小孩來做點兒事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:18.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Clean up! I'm tired of this fuckin' mess.\N{\rCHT}打掃乾淨 我真是受夠了這堆垃圾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:20.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!\N{\rCHT}快點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:21:00.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,電影片段出自歌舞天王吉恩·凱利的《It's Always Fair Weather》\N歌曲名為《I Like Myself》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:38.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,∮Why am I feeling, when things could look black∮\N{\rCHT}為什麼當一切看起來不算樂觀的時候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:44.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,∮That nothing could possibly go wrong∮\N{\rCHT}我卻覺得生活依舊美好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:49.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,∮This has been a most unusual day∮\N{\rCHT}這已經成為最特別的一天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:58.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,∮Love has made me see things in a different way∮\N{\rCHT}愛讓我們用不同的角度看待人和事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:28.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is life always this hard,\N{\rCHT}生活總是這麼艱難嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:29.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,or is it just when you're a kid?\N{\rCHT}還是只有童年時才會這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Always like this.\N{\rCHT}總是如此{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:43.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Keep it.\N{\rCHT}留著吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:55.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm going grocery shopping. You want some milk?\N{\rCHT}我要去小賣鋪買點東西 你想要點牛奶嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,One quart or two? It's two, right?\N{\rCHT}要一瓶還是兩瓶 是兩瓶 對嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:45.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,I like these calm little moments before the storm.\N{\rCHT}我真喜歡這暴風雨前短暫的平靜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:49.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,路德維希·凡·貝多芬：德國著名的音樂家 維也納古典樂派代表人物之一
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:49.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,It reminds me of Beethoven.\N{\rCHT}這讓我想到了貝多芬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:23:57.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can you hear it?\N{\rCHT}你能聽到嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:02.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's like when you put your head to the grass...\N{\rCHT}就像當你附耳到草叢中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:06.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,you can hear it growin'.You can hear the insects.\N{\rCHT}你可以聽到它們生長 聽到昆蟲爬動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.10,0:24:15.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you like Beethoven?\N{\rCHT}你喜歡貝多芬嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.70,0:24:16.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Couldn't really say.\N{\rCHT}不算喜歡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.82,0:24:17.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna play you some.\N{\rCHT}我來給你演奏一段{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.36,0:24:24.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Daddy!\N{\rCHT}爸爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.28,0:24:36.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,You better stay here.\N{\rCHT}你最好待在這兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.26,0:24:46.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Daddy! Daddy!\N{\rCHT}爸爸 爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.67,0:25:10.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,背景音樂為艾瑞克·塞拉的原創音樂《Noon》 並非貝多芬的交響樂作品
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.02,0:25:20.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,We said noon.\N{\rCHT}我們說好了正午{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.74,0:25:25.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've got one minute past.\N{\rCHT}但是已經過了一分鐘了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.48,0:25:31.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't like Beethoven.\N{\rCHT}你不喜歡貝多芬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.14,0:25:35.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't know what you're missing.\N{\rCHT}你不知道你錯過了什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.20,0:25:39.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Overtures like that get my juices flowing.\N{\rCHT}那樣的前奏就能讓我熱血沸騰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.68,0:25:41.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,So powerful.\N{\rCHT}充滿能量{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.28,0:25:46.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,But after his openings, to be honest...\N{\rCHT}但是前奏過後 說真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.32,0:25:49.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,he does tend to get a little fucking boring.\N{\rCHT}就開始有點太他媽無聊了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.98,0:25:55.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's why I stopped!\N{\rCHT}所以我停下了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.76,0:26:01.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Toss the apartment.\N{\rCHT}徹查這間屋子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.12,0:26:26.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,沃爾夫岡·阿瑪多伊斯·莫札特：歐洲著名古典主義音樂作曲家
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.12,0:26:26.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're a Mozart fan. I love him too.\N{\rCHT}你是莫札特的粉絲 我也喜歡他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.10,0:26:29.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,I love Mozart!\N{\rCHT}我超愛莫札特的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.34,0:26:36.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,He was Austrian, you know.\N{\rCHT}他是奧地利人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.48,0:26:41.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,But for this kind of work, he's a little bit light.\N{\rCHT}但是做這種工作 他有點太輕柔了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.90,0:26:44.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I tend to go for the heavier guys.\N{\rCHT}所以我選了些更激烈的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.12,0:26:46.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cool.\N{\rCHT}不錯誒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.76,0:26:48.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dude, what the fuck are you doing?\N{\rCHT}該死的 你在幹什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.68,0:26:50.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Man, keep your bombacut mouth shut.\N{\rCHT}閉上你的臭嘴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.76,0:26:53.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,約翰內斯·勃拉姆斯：德國古典主義最後的作曲家 浪漫主義中期作曲家
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.76,0:26:53.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Check out Brahms. He's good too.\N{\rCHT}你可以試試勃拉姆斯 他也不錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.96,0:26:56.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the fuck do you know about music?\N{\rCHT}你他媽懂什麼音樂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.52,0:26:57.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Man, knock it off!\N{\rCHT}夥計 消停點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.62,0:27:13.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,You check the mattress?\N{\rCHT}你查了床墊嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.62,0:27:14.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nope.\N{\rCHT}沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.78,0:28:21.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh! Fuck! - He's dead.\N{\rCHT}- 噢 該死 - 他已經死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.80,0:28:22.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stan\N{\rCHT}史丹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.60,0:28:28.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus. Look what you did.\N{\rCHT}天 看你做了什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.20,0:28:28.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stan, you all right?\N{\rCHT}史丹 你還好嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.78,0:28:30.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look what you did.\N{\rCHT}你看你做了什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.02,0:28:51.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, Stan, Stan, what are you doin'?\N{\rCHT}嘿 史丹 你在做什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.02,0:28:53.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you doin'. He's dead!\N{\rCHT}你在做什麼 他已經死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.72,0:28:55.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,But he ruined my suit.\N{\rCHT}但是他毀了我的西裝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.12,0:28:59.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know, but he's dead.\N{\rCHT}我知道 但是他已經死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.24,0:29:02.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's a piece of meat. Forget about it. Calm down.\N{\rCHT}他現在就是一灘肉 別想了 冷靜點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.64,0:29:03.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm calm.\N{\rCHT}我很冷靜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.10,0:29:06.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Stay there, OK? - OK\N{\rCHT}- 在這待著 成嗎 - 好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.84,0:29:10.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Benny!\N{\rCHT}本尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.56,0:29:13.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Benny!\N{\rCHT}本尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.76,0:29:16.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus fuckin' Christ, Benny!\N{\rCHT}我的天 本尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.06,0:29:19.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's Malky and Stan!\N{\rCHT}我們是瑪律奇和史丹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.58,0:29:24.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, all right?Come on.\N{\rCHT}放輕鬆 好嗎 來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.86,0:29:26.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Benny!\N{\rCHT}本尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.66,0:29:30.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get a cigarette. All right?\N{\rCHT}來 去抽根煙 好嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.96,0:29:33.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Benny, we're comin' out!\N{\rCHT}本尼 我們要過來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.82,0:29:36.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Benny, don't fire!\N{\rCHT}本尼 別開槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.98,0:29:41.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get in there!Jesus fuckin' Christ, Benny!\N{\rCHT}進去 我的天 本尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.50,0:29:44.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,You wear somethin' new and... Got a light?\N{\rCHT}你穿了新衣服 有火嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.48,0:29:48.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take it easy.\N{\rCHT}放輕鬆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.72,0:29:51.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's happening out there?\N{\rCHT}外面發生什麼了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.34,0:29:53.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's all right, ma'am. D.E.A. Police.\N{\rCHT}沒什麼 夫人 我們是緝毒組的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.70,0:29:56.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leave that poor family alone.\N{\rCHT}放過那可憐的一家吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.48,0:29:57.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Everything's all right. Just calm down\N{\rCHT}一切都好著呢 只要你冷靜下來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.92,0:29:59.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,I am calm. I'm calm.\N{\rCHT}我很冷靜 我超冷靜的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.12,0:30:01.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why don't you leave them alone?\N{\rCHT}你們為什麼不能放過他們呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.14,0:30:06.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,He said go back inside.\N{\rCHT}他說了 回你屋去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.74,0:30:14.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stan, I think it's better if we go inside.\N{\rCHT}史丹 我覺得我們還是進去比較好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.68,0:30:36.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Benny, turn that kitchen upside down! Find that shit!\N{\rCHT}本尼 把廚房掀了也要給我找出那些東西來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.64,0:30:39.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Willy Blood, look what you did!\N{\rCHT}威利·布拉德 看看你都做了什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.32,0:30:41.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,You killed a 4-year-old kid!\N{\rCHT}你殺了一個4歲小孩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.48,0:30:43.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did you really have to do that?\N{\rCHT}有必要嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.82,0:31:00.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please open the door.\N{\rCHT}求你開開門{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.54,0:31:08.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please\N{\rCHT}拜託{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.18,0:31:16.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please\N{\rCHT}求你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.60,0:32:00.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Benny, there are three kids here.\N{\rCHT}本尼 他們家有三個小孩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.17,0:32:03.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think Stan killed this girl.\N{\rCHT}我覺得史丹殺了這個女孩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.52,0:32:05.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Willy, that asshole, shot the little boy.\N{\rCHT}混蛋威利 殺了這個小男孩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.34,0:32:08.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,The third one's missing. Find her.\N{\rCHT}第三個不見了 找到她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.67,0:32:20.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit. We missed the little girl, man.\N{\rCHT}該死 我們丟了那個小女孩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.92,0:32:23.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna find the fuckin' super in this goddamn building.\N{\rCHT}為了找這小混球我要翻遍這棟樓了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.23,0:32:55.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Don't you recognize me - Me, Repugnus, know you\N{\rCHT}- 你不認識我了嗎 - 我暴亂獸 知道你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.76,0:33:10.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yo! I found it!\N{\rCHT}喲 我找到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.96,0:33:11.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bingo!\N{\rCHT}棒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.10,0:33:13.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stan, they found it\N{\rCHT}史丹 他們找到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.66,0:33:14.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know.\N{\rCHT}我知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.88,0:33:17.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,There it is.\N{\rCHT}就是這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.52,0:33:20.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's cops outside. We better go.\N{\rCHT}員警來了 我們最好撤{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.56,0:33:23.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's the cops outside. We better go. You stay here.\N{\rCHT}員警來了 我們最好撤 你留這{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.62,0:33:28.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you want me tell them?\N{\rCHT}你想我怎麼跟他們說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.62,0:33:40.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tell them...\N{\rCHT}告訴他們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.30,0:33:45.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,we were doing our job.\N{\rCHT}我們是執行公務{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.24,0:33:56.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's your name?\N{\rCHT}你叫什麼名字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.44,0:33:58.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mathilda\N{\rCHT}瑪蒂爾達{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.10,0:34:06.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sorry about your father.\N{\rCHT}關於你爸爸 我很抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.52,0:34:08.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,If somebody didn't do it one day or another,\N{\rCHT}如果他們不殺他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.46,0:34:09.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,I would have probably done it myself.\N{\rCHT}說不定哪天我自己就動手了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.64,0:34:13.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your mother, she...\N{\rCHT}你媽媽 她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.90,0:34:14.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's not my mother.\N{\rCHT}她不是我媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.86,0:34:18.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,My sister wanted to lose some weight anyway.\N{\rCHT}我姐姐一天到晚就想著減肥{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.70,0:34:21.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bet she never looked better.\N{\rCHT}但是她從沒瘦下來過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.50,0:34:23.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's not even my real sister.\N{\rCHT}她甚至不是我親姐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.80,0:34:24.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just a half sister.\N{\rCHT}只有一半是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.62,0:34:26.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not a good half at that.\N{\rCHT}還不是好的那一半{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.32,0:34:39.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you couldn't stand them, why are you crying?\N{\rCHT}如果你不喜歡他們 你哭什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.14,0:34:40.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because they killed my brother.\N{\rCHT}因為他們殺了我的弟弟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.28,0:34:45.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the hell did he do? He was four years old.\N{\rCHT}他到底做錯了什麼 他才4歲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.38,0:34:48.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,He never used to cry.\N{\rCHT}他以前從來不哭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.76,0:34:51.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,He just used to sit next to me and cuddle.\N{\rCHT}他只會坐在我旁邊 靠著我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.56,0:34:55.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was more of a mother to him\N{\rCHT}比起那頭臭母豬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.40,0:34:57.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,than that goddamned pig ever was.\N{\rCHT}我更像他的媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.84,0:34:59.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like that about pigs.\N{\rCHT}不要這樣說豬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.10,0:35:01.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're usually nicer than people.\N{\rCHT}它們通常比人好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.64,0:35:04.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,But they smell like shit.\N{\rCHT}但它們聞起來臭死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.26,0:35:07.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not true.\N{\rCHT}不對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.00,0:35:10.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, right now\N{\rCHT}事實上 現在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.26,0:35:16.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have one in my kitchen that's very clean...it smells very nice.\N{\rCHT}我廚房裡就有一頭非常乾淨的 聞起來也很香的豬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.78,0:35:18.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't have a pig in your kitchen.\N{\rCHT}你廚房裡沒有豬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.08,0:35:22.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.\N{\rCHT}我有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.26,0:35:25.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was just in there, and I didn't see any goddamned pig.\N{\rCHT}我剛剛就在那 沒有看見什麼見鬼的豬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.08,0:35:27.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't move. I'll get him.\N{\rCHT}別動 我去找它{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.80,0:35:33.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Piggy, piggy where are you?\N{\rCHT}小豬 小豬 你在哪兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.12,0:35:35.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,There you are.\N{\rCHT}原來在這兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.24,0:35:45.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mathilda.\N{\rCHT}嗨 瑪蒂爾達{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.48,0:35:47.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hi, piggy.\N{\rCHT}嗨 小豬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.02,0:35:58.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,How are you today?\N{\rCHT}今天過得好嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.12,0:36:01.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've seen better days.\N{\rCHT}並不好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.98,0:36:11.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's your name?\N{\rCHT}你叫什麼名字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.98,0:36:13.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leon.\N{\rCHT}里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.74,0:36:18.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cute name.\N{\rCHT}名字真可愛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.36,0:36:26.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,You have anyone to go to,\N{\rCHT}你有其他人可以求助{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.88,0:36:29.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,any family anyplace else?\N{\rCHT}其他家庭或者地方可去嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.36,0:36:43.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get some more milk.\N{\rCHT}我還得去拿點牛奶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.72,0:37:03.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Holy shit.\N{\rCHT}我的天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.62,0:37:11.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't touch that, please.\N{\rCHT}別碰那個 拜託{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.44,0:37:15.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leon, what exactly do you do for a living?\N{\rCHT}里昂 你究竟是做什麼工作的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.96,0:37:17.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cleaner.\N{\rCHT}清道夫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.86,0:37:21.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,You mean you're a hit man?\N{\rCHT}意思是 你是職業殺手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.68,0:37:23.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}嗯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.44,0:37:26.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cool.\N{\rCHT}酷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.66,0:37:40.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you clean anyone?\N{\rCHT}無論誰都清除嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.20,0:37:43.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,No women, no kids. That's the rules.\N{\rCHT}不殺女人和小孩兒 這是原則{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.98,0:37:46.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,How much would it cost to hire someone to get those dirtbags...\N{\rCHT}雇人殺掉那些殺了我弟弟的人渣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.18,0:37:48.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,who killed my brother?\N{\rCHT}要花多少錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.14,0:37:51.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Five grand a head.\N{\rCHT}一個人頭五千美金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.42,0:37:57.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,How about this.I work for you...\N{\rCHT}這樣好不好 我為你工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.00,0:38:01.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,and in exchange, you teach me how to clean?\N{\rCHT}作為交換 你教我怎麼殺人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.28,0:38:04.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you think?\N{\rCHT}你覺得怎麼樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.98,0:38:06.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll clean your place. I'll do the shopping.\N{\rCHT}我給你打掃屋子 出門採購{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.02,0:38:08.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll even wash your clothes.\N{\rCHT}我還會給你洗衣服{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.32,0:38:11.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is it a deal?\N{\rCHT}幹不幹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.28,0:38:14.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, it's not a deal.\N{\rCHT}不 這買賣我不幹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.38,0:38:27.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do? I've got no place to go.\N{\rCHT}那你讓我怎麼辦 我沒地方可去了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.24,0:38:31.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,You've had a rough day today.\N{\rCHT}你經歷了可怕的一天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.04,0:38:36.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep, and we'll see tomorrow,OK?\N{\rCHT}去睡一覺 我們明天再商量 好嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.74,0:38:54.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,You've been really great with me, Leon...\N{\rCHT}你對我真好 里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.38,0:38:56.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,and it's not always like that.\N{\rCHT}沒人對我這麼好過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.50,0:38:58.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know?\N{\rCHT}你知道嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.34,0:39:08.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good night.\N{\rCHT}晚安{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.20,0:40:27.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,You sleep well?\N{\rCHT}睡得好嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.35,0:40:30.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good. After breakfast you gotta take off.\N{\rCHT}好 吃過早飯之後你就得走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.98,0:40:31.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where to?\N{\rCHT}去哪裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.04,0:40:33.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not my problem.\N{\rCHT}和我無關{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.64,0:40:50.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Read it.\N{\rCHT}讀這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.74,0:40:59.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't know how to read.\N{\rCHT}你不識字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.62,0:41:03.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm learning, but I've had a lot of work lately...\N{\rCHT}我正在學 但是最近工作太忙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.43,0:41:07.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,so I'm a little behind.What's it say?\N{\rCHT}所以學得有點慢 上面說了什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.24,0:41:09.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've decided what to do with my life.\N{\rCHT}我已經決定這輩子要做什麼了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.90,0:41:11.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wanna be a cleaner.\N{\rCHT}我要做一名清道夫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.08,0:41:16.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,You wanna be a cleaner. Here.Take it.\N{\rCHT}你想做一名清道夫 給 拿著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.97,0:41:19.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a good - bye gift. Go clean,\N{\rCHT}給你的送別禮 去殺人吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.95,0:41:22.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,but not with me. I work alone. Understand? Alone.\N{\rCHT}但是別和我一起 我單獨行動 明白嗎 單獨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.75,0:41:24.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,邦妮·派克和克萊德·巴羅：電影《雌雄大盜》主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.75,0:41:24.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bonnie and Clyde didn't work alone.\N{\rCHT}邦妮和克萊德不會單獨行動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.43,0:41:27.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,塞爾瑪和路易士：電影《末路狂花》主人公 因在旅行中意外殺人而逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.43,0:41:27.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thelma and Louise didn't work alone. And they were the best.\N{\rCHT}塞爾瑪和路易士不會單獨行動 而且 她們最厲害{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.40,0:41:33.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mathilda, why are you doing this to me?\N{\rCHT}瑪蒂爾達 你為什麼要這麼對我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.82,0:41:35.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've been nothing but nice to you.\N{\rCHT}我一直對你挺好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.88,0:41:39.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,I even saved your life yesterday, right outside the door.\N{\rCHT}甚至昨天還救了你一命 就在門外面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.54,0:41:42.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Right. So now you're responsible for it.\N{\rCHT}沒錯 所以現在你就要為此負責{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.80,0:41:45.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you saved my life, you must've saved it for a good reason.\N{\rCHT}你既然救了我 你肯定有救的理由{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.30,0:41:47.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you throw me out now,\N{\rCHT}如果你現在丟下我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.20,0:41:48.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,I take it you never opened your door\N{\rCHT}那就相當於你從沒開過門{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.20,0:41:51.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,like you let me die right there in front of it.\N{\rCHT}那時就已讓我死在了你門口{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.32,0:41:53.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,But you did open it.\N{\rCHT}但是 你開了門{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.34,0:41:56.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,So...\N{\rCHT}所以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.32,0:42:04.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you don't help me, I'll die tonight. I can feel it.\N{\rCHT}如果你不幫我 今晚我就會死 我能預知到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.96,0:42:06.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna die tonight.\N{\rCHT}今晚我還不想死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.88,0:42:12.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're just a little girl, So\N{\rCHT}你還只是個小女孩 所以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.34,0:42:14.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't take it badly, but I don't think you could do it.\N{\rCHT}別難過 但我不覺得你能當個殺手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.20,0:42:16.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}對不起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.66,0:42:36.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,How's that?\N{\rCHT}怎麼樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.24,0:43:14.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mathilda, don't you ever do that again or I'll break your head.\N{\rCHT}瑪蒂爾達 你要是再敢那麼做 我就打爆你的頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.70,0:43:16.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You got that? - Okay.\N{\rCHT}- 明白了嗎 - 好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.14,0:43:20.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't work like that. It's not professional.\N{\rCHT}我不是那樣工作的 那不專業{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.64,0:43:22.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,There is rules.\N{\rCHT}要有原則{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.74,0:43:23.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\rCHT}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.02,0:43:26.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,And stop saying "Okay" All the time OK?\N{\rCHT}不要總是說"好的"了 懂嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.78,0:43:28.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\rCHT}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.64,0:43:30.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good.\N{\rCHT}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.82,0:43:48.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,You expect to use that in this hotel?\N{\rCHT}你打算在旅館里拉小提琴嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.92,0:43:53.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mister, I have to use it...\N{\rCHT}先生 我必須要拉 因為{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.14,0:43:57.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,茱莉亞音樂學院：美國著名音樂學院 為8至18歲藝術天才提供系統專業的音樂教育
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.14,0:43:57.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,because I have an audition at Juilliard next month\N{\rCHT}因為 下個月我在茱莉亞音樂學院有一場試演{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.34,0:44:00.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I have to practice.\N{\rCHT}所以 我必須要練習{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.32,0:44:04.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, but not after 10:00.\N{\rCHT}好吧 不過不能在十點之後{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.24,0:44:05.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, I promise.\N{\rCHT}好的 我保證{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.50,0:44:11.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right.I'll put you at the end of the hall...\N{\rCHT}好吧 我會把你們安排在走廊盡頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.60,0:44:13.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,so that you don't disturb anyone.\N{\rCHT}這樣就不會打擾到別人了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.16,0:44:18.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fill those out, please.\N{\rCHT}請您填了這些表格{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.10,0:44:22.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Daddy,\N{\rCHT}爸爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.38,0:44:24.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,can I please fill them out?\N{\rCHT}可以讓我填表格嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.48,0:44:26.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know how I like to check in to hotels.\N{\rCHT}你知道我很喜歡登記入住資訊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.96,0:44:32.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Pop. I'll bring these back in a minute.\N{\rCHT}謝謝爸爸 我很快會把表格拿回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.52,0:44:33.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,The fourth floor!\N{\rCHT}在四樓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.42,0:44:35.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thanks, mister!\N{\rCHT}謝謝您 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.44,0:44:37.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're lucky to have a little girl\N{\rCHT}你很幸運 有一個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.98,0:44:40.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,that's interested in things.\N{\rCHT}對一切都感興趣的女兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.58,0:44:45.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have a kid, 17, does nothing all day long.\N{\rCHT}我有個孩子 17歲 整天無所事事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.88,0:44:52.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can I leave my plant here\N{\rCHT}我能把植物留在這兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.10,0:44:53.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,while I take my stuff upstairs?\N{\rCHT}上樓放行李嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.24,0:44:55.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Of course.\N{\rCHT}當然{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.18,0:45:19.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm putting in a name of a girl in my class who makes me sick.\N{\rCHT}我填的是班裡一個我討厭的女生的名字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.42,0:45:25.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,If things get hot, she'll take the heat.\N{\rCHT}這樣出了麻煩 就由她來擔著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.54,0:45:45.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,There. Finished.\N{\rCHT}給你 填完了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.26,0:45:47.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,How old are you?\N{\rCHT}你多大了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.74,0:45:48.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Eighteen.\N{\rCHT}十八{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.84,0:45:51.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Eighteen?\N{\rCHT}十八{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.76,0:45:53.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Want to see my license?\N{\rCHT}要看看我的身份證嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.78,0:45:58.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,No. You just look a little younger.\N{\rCHT}不用 只是你看上去要小一點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.82,0:45:59.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thanks.\N{\rCHT}謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.68,0:46:11.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leon, I want you to teach me how to be like you.\N{\rCHT}里昂 我想讓你教我怎麼變得和你一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.76,0:46:15.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I want to be strong and smart like you. - Mathilda\N{\rCHT}- 我想像你一樣 強大又聰明 - 瑪蒂爾達{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.32,0:46:17.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know I'm not strong enough yet...\N{\rCHT}我知道自己現在還不夠強大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.56,0:46:21.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,but I could learn the basics, the theory.\N{\rCHT}但是我可以先打基礎 從理論學起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.48,0:46:25.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Just the theory.\N{\rCHT}你覺得呢 只是理論{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.24,0:46:32.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,I need this, Leon.I need time to get my head together.\N{\rCHT}我需要這麼做 里昂 我需要時間穩定情緒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.70,0:46:34.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I need...\N{\rCHT}好吧 而我需要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.84,0:46:43.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,a drink.\N{\rCHT}喝一杯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.94,0:46:46.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't move. I'll go get one.\N{\rCHT}別動 我去給你拿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.22,0:47:14.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,When you told me to get this baby out for you...\N{\rCHT}聽到你說讓我拿這個玩具給你的時候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.82,0:47:16.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,I thought my hearin' was goin'.\N{\rCHT}我還以為自己的耳朵出問題了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.02,0:47:19.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I says to myself, " Leon's a pro.\N{\rCHT}我告訴自己 里昂是專業的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.46,0:47:21.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nobody uses that except beginners."\N{\rCHT}只有菜鳥才用這東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.08,0:47:23.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,I like to stay in shape.\N{\rCHT}我想要保持狀態{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.02,0:47:24.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sure.\N{\rCHT}沒錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.20,0:47:29.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Always stay on top of it.It's like me.\N{\rCHT}永遠掌控一切 和我一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.02,0:47:30.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,I gotta know where everything is all the time.\N{\rCHT}任何時刻我都要知道所有東西在哪裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.50,0:47:34.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's why I never leave this place, except to go from here to there.\N{\rCHT}這就是為什麼我從來沒離開過這裡 除了走來走去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.12,0:47:41.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Change ain't good, Leon. You know?\N{\rCHT}改變不是件好事 里昂 你懂嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.00,0:47:45.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}嗯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.00,0:47:52.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Check it.\N{\rCHT}檢查一下吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.32,0:47:56.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Make sure it's the right thing.\N{\rCHT}確認這就是你要的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.76,0:47:57.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,I trust you.\N{\rCHT}我相信你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.64,0:47:59.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,One thing's got nothin' to do with the other.\N{\rCHT}一碼是一碼 事情要分開算{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.86,0:48:01.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Remember that.\N{\rCHT}記住這一點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.18,0:48:03.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,I will.\N{\rCHT}我會的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.06,0:48:22.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,The rifle is the first weapon you learn how to use...\N{\rCHT}來福槍是你要學習的第一件武器{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.40,0:48:25.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,because it lets you keep your distance from the client.\N{\rCHT}因為它能讓你和目標保持距離{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.98,0:48:28.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,The closer you get to being a pro...\N{\rCHT}當你越來越專業時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.46,0:48:30.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,the closer you can get to the client.\N{\rCHT}你離目標也就越來越近{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.66,0:48:33.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,The knife, for example,\N{\rCHT}拿刀來舉個例子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.68,0:48:35.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,is the last thing you learn.\N{\rCHT}刀是你要學習的最後一件武器{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.58,0:48:37.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay?\N{\rCHT}明白嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.56,0:48:39.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\rCHT}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.94,0:48:41.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Position.\N{\rCHT}找位置{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.98,0:49:04.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rCHT}不對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.36,0:49:08.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Never take it off until the last minute.\N{\rCHT}不到最後一刻 別把鏡蓋拿下來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.34,0:49:09.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,It reflects light.\N{\rCHT}它(瞄準鏡)會反射光線{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.60,0:49:12.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,They can see you coming from a mile away.\N{\rCHT}他們在一英里外都能看到你來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.32,0:49:16.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,And always dress down.\N{\rCHT}還有 記得永遠穿著低調{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.12,0:49:19.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Never brighter than the floor, okay?\N{\rCHT}比地板還要暗淡 明白嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.68,0:49:21.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\rCHT}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.54,0:49:26.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's practice now. It's the best way to learn.\N{\rCHT}現在我們來練習 這是學習的最好辦法了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.84,0:49:29.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Who should I hit?\N{\rCHT}我該射誰呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.06,0:49:31.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Whoever.\N{\rCHT}誰都行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.62,0:49:39.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll be with you in a second.\N{\rCHT}我一會就來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.52,0:49:40.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Give me a few minutes.\N{\rCHT}等我一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.24,0:49:41.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.02,0:49:43.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,You guys get lost. I don't want to see you.\N{\rCHT}你們怎麼就不懂呢 我不要看見你們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.08,0:49:46.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,This has to look natural.\N{\rCHT}看上去得自然{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.64,0:49:58.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,No women, no kids. Right?\N{\rCHT}不殺女人和小孩兒 對嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.80,0:49:59.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Right.\N{\rCHT}對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.56,0:50:09.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jogger in the yellow and orange?\N{\rCHT}那個穿橙黃相間外套 在慢跑的人怎麼樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.88,0:50:10.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\rCHT}可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.26,0:50:15.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Keep calm.\N{\rCHT}保持冷靜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.28,0:50:21.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't take your eyes off him.\N{\rCHT}視線不要離開目標{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.98,0:50:24.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Breathe easy.\N{\rCHT}放慢呼吸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.48,0:50:28.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Watch his movement.\N{\rCHT}觀察他的動作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.66,0:50:33.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Pretend you're running with him.\N{\rCHT}假裝你跟他一起在跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.86,0:50:39.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Try to feel his next movement.\N{\rCHT}試著感受他的下一個動作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.80,0:50:43.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take a deep breath. Hold it.\N{\rCHT}深呼吸 屏息{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.66,0:50:54.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now.\N{\rCHT}開槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.90,0:50:58.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm all right. I'm fine.\N{\rCHT}我沒事 我很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.90,0:51:00.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get down!\N{\rCHT}趴下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.96,0:51:02.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,One shot. Not bad, huh?\N{\rCHT}一擊命中 不錯吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.62,0:51:09.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can we try with real bullets now?\N{\rCHT}現在能用真子彈了嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.82,0:51:12.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not today. Let's pack up.\N{\rCHT}今天不行 收工{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.12,0:51:22.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Like that.\N{\rCHT}就像這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.70,0:52:07.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, thanks.\N{\rCHT}不用 謝了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.18,0:52:09.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,No discussion.\N{\rCHT}沒得商量{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.28,0:52:55.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,"It seemed to Socrates..."\N{\rCHT}蘇格拉底似乎…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.04,0:53:05.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.\N{\rCHT}我來吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.76,0:53:21.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leon, all we do is work.\N{\rCHT}里昂 我們整天都在工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.46,0:53:25.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,We need a break. Let's play a game.\N{\rCHT}休息一下 來玩個遊戲吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.24,0:53:27.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,What kind of game?\N{\rCHT}什麼遊戲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.56,0:53:29.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have this great game.\N{\rCHT}我有個超棒的遊戲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.46,0:53:31.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,It makes you think and helps your memory.\N{\rCHT}有助於思考和記憶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.88,0:53:33.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's exactly what you need.\N{\rCHT}正是你所需要的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.24,0:53:37.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\rCHT}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.38,0:53:59.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Who is it?\N{\rCHT}我是誰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.93,0:54:01.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,歌手麥當娜1984年發行的經典曲目 《Like A Virgin》
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.93,0:54:01.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\N{\rCHT}不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.52,0:54:23.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,1962年 瑪麗蓮·夢露為即將迎來45歲生日的甘迺迪總統獻唱生日歌
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.52,0:54:23.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\N{\rCHT}不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.60,0:54:33.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Moustache.\N{\rCHT}小鬍子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.36,0:54:38.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,這個是在模仿喜劇大師卓別林
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.36,0:54:38.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rCHT}不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.69,0:54:47.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,吉恩·凱利在1952年上映的經典電影《雨中曲》中的歌舞表演
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.69,0:54:47.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gene Kelly?\N{\rCHT}吉恩·凱利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.52,0:54:50.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good.\N{\rCHT}答對了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.96,0:54:52.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your turn now.\N{\rCHT}輪到你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.92,0:55:00.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, pilgrim.\N{\rCHT}好了 你們這些旅客{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.36,0:55:05.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Clint Eastwood?\N{\rCHT}克林特·伊斯特伍德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.67,0:55:06.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,克林特·伊斯特伍德 硬漢明星 被稱為"城市牛仔"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.44,0:55:14.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I give up.\N{\rCHT}我不知道 我放棄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.71,0:55:17.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,約翰·韋恩：著名的好萊塢西部片明星
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.71,0:55:17.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,John Wayne.\N{\rCHT}約翰·韋恩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.22,0:55:19.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was just about to say that.\N{\rCHT}我剛剛想說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.54,0:55:23.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,I swear. It's amazing.Leon, really brilliant.\N{\rCHT}我發誓 太神奇了 里昂 你扮得太像了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.52,0:55:27.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Amazing\N{\rCHT}太棒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.08,0:55:44.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,You love your plant, don't you?\N{\rCHT}你很喜歡你的盆栽 對嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.90,0:55:46.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's my best friend.\N{\rCHT}它是我最好的朋友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.80,0:55:50.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Always happy. No questions.\N{\rCHT}永遠快樂 無憂無慮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.80,0:55:57.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's like me, you see.No roots.\N{\rCHT}就像我一樣 沒有根{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.10,0:55:59.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you really love it, you should plant it\N{\rCHT}如果你真喜歡它 就應該把它{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.82,0:56:02.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,in a park so it can have roots.\N{\rCHT}種在公園裡 讓它落地生根{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.98,0:56:05.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leon\N{\rCHT}里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.08,0:56:09.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,You should be watering me if you want me to grow.\N{\rCHT}同樣你想讓我長大 也該為我澆水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.20,0:56:11.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're right.\N{\rCHT}沒錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.96,0:56:43.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,They gotta be jumping out of the plate. They gotta be alive.\N{\rCHT}它們要能從盤子裡跳出來 要夠新鮮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.44,0:56:54.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Leon.\N{\rCHT}好久不見 里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.96,0:57:01.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,I missed you.\N{\rCHT}我想你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.28,0:57:05.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you missed some nice jobs too.\N{\rCHT}你也錯過了一些好工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.38,0:57:07.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,Been training.\N{\rCHT}我在訓練{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.61,0:57:12.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Training's good, but don't overdo it.\N{\rCHT}訓練是好事 但別過頭了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.09,0:57:14.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Training don't pay as good as working, Leon.\N{\rCHT}工作可比訓練賺得多 里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.02,0:57:15.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tony...\N{\rCHT}托尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.80,0:57:23.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,all the money I make, that you keep for me...\N{\rCHT}我賺的那些錢 你幫我保管的錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.96,0:57:25.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,You need some money?\N{\rCHT}你需要用錢嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.84,0:57:27.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just curious.\N{\rCHT}我就是問一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.76,0:57:29.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've been working a long time...\N{\rCHT}我為你工作這麼久{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.10,0:57:31.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I haven't done anything with my money.\N{\rCHT}從來沒用過那些錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.08,0:57:37.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe someday\N{\rCHT}我想也許有一天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.52,0:57:40.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,I could use it.\N{\rCHT}我會用到它{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.25,0:57:43.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,You met a woman.\N{\rCHT}你有女人了嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.66,0:57:54.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,You gotta be careful with women.\N{\rCHT}你要小心女人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.62,0:57:57.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Remember when you arrived in this country?\N{\rCHT}記得你剛來這個國家的時候嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.04,0:57:59.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,When I took you in,\N{\rCHT}我收留你的時候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.32,0:58:02.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,you were still wet behind the fuckin' ears...\N{\rCHT}你還是個毛頭小子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.64,0:58:05.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,and, already, you were in deep shit because of a woman.\N{\rCHT}卻已經因為女人趟進了渾水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.72,0:58:07.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that, Leon.\N{\rCHT}別忘了 里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.52,0:58:09.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wish I could sometimes.\N{\rCHT}有時我真希望我能忘了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.04,0:58:15.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, about my money...\N{\rCHT}你知道 我的錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.98,0:58:21.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could give a little\N{\rCHT}也許我可以分一點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.58,0:58:24.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,to someone.\N{\rCHT}給別人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.80,0:58:29.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, to help out.\N{\rCHT}去幫助別人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.56,0:58:35.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's your money. I'm just holding it for you, like a bank.\N{\rCHT}這是你的錢 我只是替你保管 像銀行一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.46,0:58:37.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Except better than a bank\N{\rCHT}但我比銀行好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.78,0:58:39.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,because banks always get knocked off.\N{\rCHT}銀行經常會被搶劫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.26,0:58:42.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,No one knocks off old Tony.\N{\rCHT}沒人搶得了老托尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.40,0:58:44.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Besides, with a bank...\N{\rCHT}此外 把錢存進銀行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.18,0:58:47.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,there's always tons of forms and all that shit.\N{\rCHT}有成噸的狗屁表格要填{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.50,0:58:50.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,But old Tony, nothin' to read,\N{\rCHT}在我這兒 不用看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.30,0:58:51.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,nothin' to write.\N{\rCHT}不用寫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.66,0:58:54.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's all in his head.\N{\rCHT}都在我腦子裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.62,0:58:56.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know how to read now.\N{\rCHT}現在我能識字了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.90,0:59:02.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's good, Leon, good.\N{\rCHT}那很好 里昂 很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.46,0:59:07.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your money's here. Whenever you want it,\N{\rCHT}你的錢在這兒 你需要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.08,0:59:10.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,you just ask me.Here's a grand.\N{\rCHT}就來問我拿 這裡有一千元{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.96,0:59:12.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Come on. - It's okay. I don't need it.\N{\rCHT}- 拿著 - 沒事 我不需要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.62,0:59:15.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take it. Have some fun. Go ahead.\N{\rCHT}拿去吧 找點樂子 拿著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.58,0:59:16.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.98,0:59:17.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right.\N{\rCHT}好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.50,0:59:22.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now let's talk business.Don't move.\N{\rCHT}現在我們來談談生意 別走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.08,0:59:23.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll go get the file.\N{\rCHT}我去拿資料{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.92,0:59:27.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Manolo, a glass of milk for my friend Leon here.\N{\rCHT}馬諾洛 給我朋友里昂來杯牛奶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.14,0:59:54.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Listen, Mathilda, you better be careful.\N{\rCHT}聽著 瑪蒂爾達 你最好小心點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.82,0:59:56.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can't just speak to any guy off the street.\N{\rCHT}不要隨便跟街上的陌生人講話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.50,1:00:01.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leon, get a grip. What's the big fucking deal?\N{\rCHT}里昂 緊張什麼 這他媽有什麼大不了的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.62,1:00:03.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was just smoking a butt while I was waiting.\N{\rCHT}我只是在等你的時候 借根煙抽抽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.84,1:00:07.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want you to stop cursing.\N{\rCHT}我不許你講髒話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.24,1:00:10.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can't talk to people like that all the time.\N{\rCHT}你不能總這樣和別人交談{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.66,1:00:13.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want you to make an effort to talk nice.\N{\rCHT}我要你學著好好講話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.32,1:00:21.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I want you to stop smoking. It will kill you.\N{\rCHT}還有 我希望你把煙戒了 這會要了你的命的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.69,1:00:24.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay\N{\rCHT}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.27,1:00:30.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stay away from him. He looks like a weirdo.\N{\rCHT}離他遠一點 他不像好人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.61,1:00:34.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay\N{\rCHT}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.08,1:00:38.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll be out in five minutes. Stand where I can see you.\N{\rCHT}我五分鐘後出來 站在我能看見你的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.20,1:00:41.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay\N{\rCHT}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.44,1:00:58.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leon, I think I'm kinda falling in love with you.\N{\rCHT}里昂 我好像有點愛上你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.76,1:01:02.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's the first time for me, you know.\N{\rCHT}我第一次有這種感覺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.24,1:01:06.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,How do you know it's love if you've never been in love before?\N{\rCHT}你從沒談過戀愛 你怎麼知道這就是愛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.76,1:01:09.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cause I feel it.\N{\rCHT}因為我感覺到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.92,1:01:11.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where?\N{\rCHT}哪兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.45,1:01:16.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,In my stomach.\N{\rCHT}在我的胃裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.00,1:01:21.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's all warm.\N{\rCHT}暖暖的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.76,1:01:28.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,I always had a knot there, and now it's gone.\N{\rCHT}我以前老是胃疼 現在不會了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.79,1:01:35.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mathilda, I'm glad you don't have a stomachache anymore.\N{\rCHT}瑪蒂爾達 我很高興你的胃病好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.20,1:01:38.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't think it means anything.\N{\rCHT}但這不能說明什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.93,1:01:43.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm late for work. I hate being late for work.\N{\rCHT}我要遲到了 我最討厭遲到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.96,1:02:29.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, How's the practicing going?\N{\rCHT}嗨 小提琴練得怎麼樣了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.04,1:03:01.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,How are we today, miss?\N{\rCHT}今天怎麼樣 小姐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.40,1:03:04.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,A little sick of practicing.\N{\rCHT}我有點厭倦練琴了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.88,1:03:06.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,I understand.\N{\rCHT}我懂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.08,1:03:08.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,But you're doing all right.\N{\rCHT}但是你做得很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.48,1:03:11.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,I haven't received any complaints.\N{\rCHT}沒有人來投訴你們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.17,1:03:16.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,I put a cloth over the strings to lessen the noise.\N{\rCHT}我在弦上放了塊布來減少噪音{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.65,1:03:18.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's very smart.\N{\rCHT}真聰明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.36,1:03:20.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not everyone loves music.\N{\rCHT}不是人人都愛音樂的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.11,1:03:21.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know.\N{\rCHT}我知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.78,1:03:25.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,What exactly does your father do?\N{\rCHT}你父親到底是做什麼的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.23,1:03:28.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's a composer.\N{\rCHT}他是作曲家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.59,1:03:30.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.\N{\rCHT}真厲害{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.78,1:03:33.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Except he's not really my father.\N{\rCHT}不過他其實不是我父親{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.26,1:03:40.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's my lover.\N{\rCHT}他是我愛人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.05,1:03:46.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Think I'll go for a walk.\N{\rCHT}我要去散步了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.86,1:04:04.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you doing Saturday night?\N{\rCHT}週六晚上你有事嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.09,1:04:05.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,What about dinner?\N{\rCHT}一起吃晚餐怎麼樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.88,1:04:07.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where you goin'?\N{\rCHT}你要去哪裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.01,1:04:09.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Visiting friends at 6J.\N{\rCHT}拜訪6樓J室的朋友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.60,1:04:10.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.\N{\rCHT}去吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.70,1:05:43.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,We know you're a busy man.\N{\rCHT}我們知道你是個大忙人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.86,1:05:45.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll make this short.\N{\rCHT}我們也想快點完事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.27,1:05:48.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you'll just take us step-by-step\N{\rCHT}你一步一步說清楚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.12,1:05:49.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,through exactly what happened.\N{\rCHT}這裡到底發生了什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.64,1:05:52.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,The guy was here. He went for his gun.\N{\rCHT}那傢伙在這兒 他要去拿他的槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.80,1:05:54.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bang, we shot him.\N{\rCHT}砰的一聲 我們打中了他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.24,1:05:59.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where exactly were the kids?\N{\rCHT}孩子們當時在哪裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.63,1:06:00.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know!\N{\rCHT}我哪知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.15,1:06:03.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,They should have been at school, don't you think?\N{\rCHT}你不覺得他們當時應該在學校麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.69,1:06:06.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your statement said you were the first man in.\N{\rCHT}你的陳述裡面說你是第一個進入屋子的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.08,1:06:07.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see any kids?\N{\rCHT}難道你沒看見孩子麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.12,1:06:08.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,The door was broken. What happened?\N{\rCHT}大門也壞了 發生了什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.65,1:06:09.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did you follow the procedure?\N{\rCHT}你是按程式來的麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.09,1:06:13.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I lost a good man here.\N{\rCHT}我失去了一個好隊員{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.55,1:06:15.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the fuck do you want with me?\N{\rCHT}你他媽的到底想讓我怎麼樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.00,1:06:17.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cooperation.\N{\rCHT}配合{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.71,1:06:25.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,I haven't got time for this Mickey Mouse bullshit!\N{\rCHT}我沒時間在這裡跟你們扯淡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.04,1:06:29.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,You want cooperation? Come up in my office, room 4602.\N{\rCHT}你想讓我配合你工作 來我辦公室 4602{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.31,1:06:43.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Kids should be at school.\N{\rCHT}孩子就應該去上學{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.49,1:06:46.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, that's my ball!\N{\rCHT}拜託 那是我的球{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.66,1:06:51.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Give that back. Where you goin'?\N{\rCHT}還給我 你去哪兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.04,1:06:54.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Damn! Where you goin', man? That's my ball!\N{\rCHT}該死 你幹什麼 那是我的球{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.88,1:07:03.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Follow the blue car.\N{\rCHT}跟著那輛藍色的車{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.98,1:07:07.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,You want me to blast the music and go through the lights?\N{\rCHT}你是讓我在鳴警笛的車面前闖紅燈麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.16,1:07:08.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, drive slowly.\N{\rCHT}不 慢慢開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.94,1:07:11.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take the hundred bucks, and shut the fuck up.\N{\rCHT}拿著這一百塊 他媽的給我閉嘴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.28,1:07:48.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I do not want to fight you, but you leave me no choice.\N{\rCHT}我不想和你打 但我別無選擇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.60,1:07:54.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Boy, you just gave me a great idea!\N{\rCHT}好孩子 你提醒了我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.35,1:07:59.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean a big one!\N{\rCHT}這辦法太好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.98,1:08:01.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Welcome back to E! News Daily...\N{\rCHT}歡迎回到E頻道 現在是每日新聞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.74,1:08:05.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,our 30-minute look at the latest in entertainment news.\N{\rCHT}現在讓我們用30分鐘的時間回顧一下娛樂大事件{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.31,1:08:06.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm Bianca Ferrar.\N{\rCHT}我是碧昂卡·費拉爾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.45,1:08:14.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's for you. A present.\N{\rCHT}這是給你的 一份禮物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.34,1:08:19.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to open it? I'll open it.\N{\rCHT}想打開麼 我來開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.13,1:08:27.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,How do you like it? Nice, eh?\N{\rCHT}怎麼樣 喜歡麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.55,1:08:30.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr. McGuffin?\N{\rCHT}麥高芬先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.70,1:08:35.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can I have a word with you?\N{\rCHT}我能跟你談談麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.36,1:09:59.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here. It's for a contract. Twenty grand, right?\N{\rCHT}這個是合同 兩萬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.72,1:10:02.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,His name is Norman Stansfield, and he's in room 4602...\N{\rCHT}他叫諾曼·史丹菲爾德 他住在4602{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.56,1:10:04.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,in the D.E.A. Building, 26 Federal Plaza.\N{\rCHT}聯邦廣場26號緝毒大樓4602{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.68,1:10:07.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not taking it.\N{\rCHT}我不收{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.18,1:10:08.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why not?\N{\rCHT}為什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.20,1:10:11.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's too heavy. Well.\N{\rCHT}錢太多了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.38,1:10:14.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Will you rent me your gear for the day?\N{\rCHT}你的槍能租給我用一天嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.46,1:10:15.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,I never lend out my gear.\N{\rCHT}我的槍從不外租{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.12,1:10:21.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,But you still have your gun. Use it.\N{\rCHT}但你不是有自己的槍麼 用那個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.16,1:10:24.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just do me a favor. Don't shoot out the window.\N{\rCHT}幫我個忙 別打碎玻璃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.50,1:10:25.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why are you so mean to me?\N{\rCHT}你對我怎麼這麼吝嗇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.30,1:10:30.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wildly killing people you don't give a shit about...\N{\rCHT}你隨便殺一些毫不在意的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.10,1:10:33.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,but you won't get the bastards that killed my whole family?\N{\rCHT}但就是不幫我解決那些殺了我全家的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.28,1:10:36.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Revenge is not good once you're done.\N{\rCHT}一旦開始復仇 就不會有好結果的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.08,1:10:40.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Believe. It's better to forget.\N{\rCHT}相信我 還是忘了好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.16,1:10:42.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Forget? After I've seen the outline\N{\rCHT}忘了 在我看到地板上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.66,1:10:44.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,of my brother's body on the floor...\N{\rCHT}我弟弟屍體的輪廓之後{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.58,1:10:45.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,you expect me to forget?\N{\rCHT}你竟然想讓我全都忘了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.64,1:10:48.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want to kill those sons of bitches.\N{\rCHT}我要殺了那些狗雜種們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.26,1:10:51.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Blow their fucking heads off.\N{\rCHT}爆他們的頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.12,1:10:52.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nothing's the same\N{\rCHT}在你殺了人之後{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.11,1:10:53.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,after you've killed someone.\N{\rCHT}一切都會不一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.86,1:10:57.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your life is changed forever.\N{\rCHT}你的人生會被完全改變{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.44,1:11:03.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,You have to sleep with one eye open for the rest of your life.\N{\rCHT}你的餘生恐怕都得睜一隻眼閉一隻眼睡覺了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.74,1:11:06.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't give a shit about sleeping, Leon.\N{\rCHT}我他媽才不在意怎麼睡覺 里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.08,1:11:11.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want love or death.\N{\rCHT}我要愛 或死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.34,1:11:14.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's it.\N{\rCHT}就這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.76,1:11:17.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want death.\N{\rCHT}我選擇死亡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.34,1:11:22.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get off my case, Mathilda. I'm tired of your games.\N{\rCHT}瑪蒂爾達 放過我吧 我對你的遊戲已經感到厭倦了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.52,1:11:28.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's this really great game, Leon.\N{\rCHT}這是個很棒的遊戲 里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.82,1:11:31.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Makes people nicer. Starts them thinking.\N{\rCHT}讓人變得聰明 學會思考{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.68,1:11:37.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,The kind of game you love.\N{\rCHT}你喜歡的那種遊戲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.46,1:11:56.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,If I win you keep me with you for life.\N{\rCHT}如果我贏了 你一輩子都不能離開我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.52,1:12:00.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,And if you lose?\N{\rCHT}如果你輸了呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.12,1:12:03.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go shopping alone, like before.\N{\rCHT}你就可以像以前一樣自己去買東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.51,1:12:07.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're gonna lose, Mathilda.\N{\rCHT}瑪蒂爾達 你一定會輸的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.56,1:12:13.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's a round in the chamber. I heard it.\N{\rCHT}子彈上膛了 我聽出來的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.50,1:12:14.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,So what?\N{\rCHT}那又怎樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.28,1:12:17.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's it to you if I end up with a bullet in the head?\N{\rCHT}要是我在你面前被子彈爆了頭 會怎樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.92,1:12:21.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nothing.\N{\rCHT}不會怎樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.22,1:12:27.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I hope you're not lying, Leon.\N{\rCHT}里昂 我希望你說的是實話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.86,1:12:32.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I really hope that deep down inside there's no love in you.\N{\rCHT}我真的希望 在你內心深處對我沒有一絲的愛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.20,1:12:40.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because if there is just a little bit of love in there for me...\N{\rCHT}因為只要在你心裡 對我有一絲的愛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.80,1:12:44.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think that in a few\N{\rCHT}幾分鐘之後{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.62,1:12:46.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,minutes you'll regret you never said anything.\N{\rCHT}你就會後悔沒有阻止我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.96,1:12:57.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,I love you, Leon.\N{\rCHT}我愛你 里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.94,1:13:16.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,I win.\N{\rCHT}我贏了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.76,1:13:38.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,I took a hit. I need a hand now.\N{\rCHT}我受傷了 需要一個幫手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.56,1:13:43.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know she's young, but she learns fast.\N{\rCHT}我知道你擔心她太年輕 但是她學得很快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.16,1:13:46.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Kids need to be shaped into something, right?\N{\rCHT}學習要從娃娃抓起 不是麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.30,1:13:48.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know. I taught you that.\N{\rCHT}我知道 這是我教你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.00,1:13:50.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,But ain't there an age limit?\N{\rCHT}但我們不是有年齡限制麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.64,1:13:51.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's 18.\N{\rCHT}她18歲了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.34,1:13:53.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Really?\N{\rCHT}真的麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.54,1:13:59.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,How about something to drink, Tony?\N{\rCHT}托尼 來點喝的吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.62,1:14:02.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sure. Manolo, glass of milk for Leon.\N{\rCHT}當然 馬諾洛 給里昂來杯牛奶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.94,1:14:06.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nice tattoo.\N{\rCHT}很棒的刺青{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.46,1:14:15.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Manolo, make that two.\N{\rCHT}馬諾洛 來兩杯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.40,1:14:35.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's that for?\N{\rCHT}那是幹嘛的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.46,1:14:37.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can't afford to catch cold.\N{\rCHT}感冒了可不好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.46,1:14:41.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,First you find out where the chain is.\N{\rCHT}首先 你得先找到門鏈子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.34,1:14:42.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can't see it, but you can feel it. Here.\N{\rCHT}你看不著 但用手能摸出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.72,1:14:45.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll ring, you start talking.\N{\rCHT}我一按門鈴 你就說話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.40,1:14:47.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do I say?\N{\rCHT}我要說什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.58,1:14:49.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Whatever you want.\N{\rCHT}什麼都行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.04,1:14:53.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes?\N{\rCHT}誰啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.84,1:14:55.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's Susan.\N{\rCHT}我 蘇珊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.48,1:14:59.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. You must have the wrong door, little girl.\N{\rCHT}不好意思 你走錯了 小姑娘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.54,1:15:00.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know any Susan.\N{\rCHT}我不認識一個叫蘇珊的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.62,1:15:04.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Move back a little. I can't see anything.\N{\rCHT}你往後站 我看不見{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.24,1:15:10.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,The light's out. It's all dark out here.\N{\rCHT}燈壞了 這裡很黑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.06,1:15:16.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mister, I'm scared.\N{\rCHT}先生 我好害怕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.08,1:15:19.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\rCHT}好啦好啦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.26,1:15:24.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the fuck are you doing?\N{\rCHT}你他媽在幹嘛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.40,1:15:32.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Open up.\N{\rCHT}張嘴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.32,1:15:37.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,If it leaves your mouth, I'll pull the trigger, capisce?\N{\rCHT}槍管離開你的嘴我就扣下扳機 明白嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.80,1:16:18.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here's okay. Let it go. I said, "Let it go."\N{\rCHT}對 就這樣 鬆開 我讓你鬆開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.38,1:16:21.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Move. Move over.\N{\rCHT}去 去那邊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.72,1:16:25.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Easy. Easy.\N{\rCHT}放鬆 別激動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.48,1:16:31.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. Your turn.\N{\rCHT}去吧 該你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.96,1:16:40.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Help me. Please don't beat me.\N{\rCHT}救命 求你別打我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.32,1:16:42.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sir?\N{\rCHT}先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.58,1:16:49.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sir, it's not my dope.\N{\rCHT}先生 那不是我的毒品{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.22,1:16:51.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sir, look l...\N{\rCHT}先生 看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.96,1:16:53.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,A little left, please. Sir, look l...\N{\rCHT}請往左邊網站好麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.96,1:17:03.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, the security shot.\N{\rCHT}為了保險起見{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.46,1:17:11.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, the second goes higher on the chest.\N{\rCHT}不 第二槍要打在胸部上方一點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.42,1:17:13.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aim for the heart and lungs.\N{\rCHT}瞄準心臟和肺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.68,1:17:16.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,There. Right there. You see?\N{\rCHT}這兒 看到了麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.18,1:17:18.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,The first shot takes him out of order.\N{\rCHT}第一槍讓他倒地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.60,1:17:20.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,The second finishes him off.\N{\rCHT}第二槍讓他歸西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.64,1:17:22.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Never in the face.\N{\rCHT}千萬別打臉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.60,1:17:25.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,If they can't recognize the client, you don't get paid.\N{\rCHT}雇主認不出他要殺的人 不會付錢的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.56,1:17:29.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,You could take out anybody and said you did the job.\N{\rCHT}因為你可以隨便殺一個人交差{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.36,1:17:30.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Got it?\N{\rCHT}懂了麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.08,1:17:32.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Got it. Never in the face.\N{\rCHT}懂了 不打臉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.62,1:17:35.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now you can put the tools away.\N{\rCHT}你現在可以把工具收起來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.24,1:17:39.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the fuck is going on? Hey, mister!\N{\rCHT}到底怎麼回事 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.34,1:17:40.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you fuckin...\N{\rCHT}草 到底怎麼回事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.80,1:17:46.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,You see, when you use the silencer a lot...\N{\rCHT}你看 當你消音器用得太久的時候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.42,1:17:49.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,you have to put a piece of cloth here...\N{\rCHT}你要在這兒墊塊布{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.70,1:17:52.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,because it gets very hot and could burn it inside.\N{\rCHT}因為它會發熱 然後裡面燒起來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.32,1:17:52.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay\N{\rCHT}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.76,1:17:55.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,A damp, black cloth is the best.\N{\rCHT}最好用一塊黑色的濕布{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.80,1:17:59.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,What you doing?\N{\rCHT}你幹什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.84,1:18:03.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,We said no women, no kids.\N{\rCHT}我們說過不殺女人和小孩兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.10,1:18:06.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Who do you think this is gonna kill, junkies and monkeys?\N{\rCHT}你知道這些毒品會害了誰嗎 並不是那些混混 地痞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.24,1:18:25.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now it's clean.\N{\rCHT}這樣就乾淨了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.82,1:18:28.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here.\N{\rCHT}走吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.26,1:18:44.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,I thought we don't have the right to drink.\N{\rCHT}我還以為我們沒權利喝酒呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.31,1:18:49.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know, but we're making an exception for your first time.\N{\rCHT}是 但是今天為你第一次幹活破一次例{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.44,1:18:55.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, if we're making exceptions for a job well-done...\N{\rCHT}既然我們可以為工作成果而破例{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.90,1:18:59.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,how about a kiss, like in the movies?\N{\rCHT}那不如像電影一樣 輕輕吻一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.62,1:19:02.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rCHT}不可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.24,1:19:04.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\rCHT}可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.16,1:19:09.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,What you doing?\N{\rCHT}你要幹嘛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.34,1:19:10.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kiss you.\N{\rCHT}我要親你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.79,1:19:12.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want you to stop, please.\N{\rCHT}不要這樣 不要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.33,1:19:14.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on. Just a kiss.\N{\rCHT}來吧 就親一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.75,1:19:21.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stop. Everyone is watching us. Go sit down.\N{\rCHT}快停下來 大家都看著呢 去坐好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.97,1:19:31.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Enjoy.\N{\rCHT}慢用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.98,1:19:39.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't believe me, do you?\N{\rCHT}你不相信我 對吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.34,1:19:40.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,How's that?\N{\rCHT}為什麼這麼說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.62,1:19:42.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,When I say I'm in love with you.\N{\rCHT}當我說我愛上你了的時候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.89,1:19:47.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mathilda, please drop it. Just change the subject, okay?\N{\rCHT}瑪蒂爾達 別說了 我們換個話題好嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.16,1:19:48.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay. Sorry.\N{\rCHT}好 好 抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.40,1:19:53.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, how old were you when you made your first hit?\N{\rCHT}那 你第一次殺人的時候多大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.60,1:19:55.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nineteen.\N{\rCHT}十九歲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.00,1:19:58.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Beat you.\N{\rCHT}比你早哦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.52,1:21:04.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,What you doing?\N{\rCHT}你在做什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.30,1:21:06.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can't afford to catch a cold.\N{\rCHT}感冒了可不好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.68,1:21:55.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's no doorbell.\N{\rCHT}這兒沒門鈴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.00,1:21:56.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,So knock on the door.\N{\rCHT}那就敲門{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.28,1:22:03.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes?\N{\rCHT}誰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.77,1:22:07.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hi. I'm looking for Mr. Reuben's apartment...\N{\rCHT}你好 我是來拜訪魯賓先生的…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.30,1:22:10.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,but it's all dark out here in the hall, and I'm lost.\N{\rCHT}但是走廊裡好黑 而且我迷路了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.51,1:22:13.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just a second.\N{\rCHT}等一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.14,1:22:29.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,You want more? Come on. Show your fucking face.\N{\rCHT}還想要麼 來吧 把你的臉露出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.11,1:22:30.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,You think you're going to get me that easily?\N{\rCHT}你們覺得那麼簡單就能殺了我嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.16,1:22:39.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,When it's tough like this, you know it's gonna be ugly.\N{\rCHT}遇到這樣強硬的對手時 場面肯定不好看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.78,1:22:40.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Better make it quick or\N{\rCHT}最好快點解決他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.80,1:22:43.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,else we'll be all day listening to his crap.\N{\rCHT}不然我們就要一直聽他廢話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.98,1:22:47.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Asshole! Come on, show me your fucking face, faggot!\N{\rCHT}混蛋 來吧 讓我看看你的臉 娘娘腔{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.34,1:22:48.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, gum trick.\N{\rCHT}再來一個口香糖的把戲啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.46,1:22:52.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey,What about the ring trick? You know that one?\N{\rCHT}嘿 你知道拉環把戲麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.84,1:22:55.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ring trick? Come on, asshole. I'm waiting.\N{\rCHT}拉環把戲嗎 來啊混蛋 我等著呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.24,1:22:56.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Show it to me, motherfucker.\N{\rCHT}給我看看啊 混帳東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.82,1:23:07.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's the ring trick.\N{\rCHT}這就是拉環把戲[手榴彈]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.71,1:23:26.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mario, go back to the barbershop. We'll finish later.\N{\rCHT}馬里奧 你先回理髮店吧 我們一會兒再剪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.39,1:23:40.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey Leon, what's up?\N{\rCHT}里昂 你好啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.89,1:23:42.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,All done already?\N{\rCHT}都解決了嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.32,1:23:43.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rCHT}沒呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.73,1:23:46.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nicer than people, eh?\N{\rCHT}這東西比人好啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.76,1:23:48.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,I told you that.\N{\rCHT}以前就告訴過你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.86,1:23:52.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,You got a problem?\N{\rCHT}你遇到麻煩了嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.89,1:23:53.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rCHT}沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.70,1:23:58.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get the chair. Sit down.\N{\rCHT}拿把椅子來 坐吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.87,1:24:07.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was thinking.\N{\rCHT}我最近在想{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.64,1:24:14.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,If something happens to me someday...\N{\rCHT}如果哪天我遇到不測{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.56,1:24:17.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, Leon, nothing's gonna happen to you.\N{\rCHT}里昂 你不會遇到不測的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.38,1:24:20.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're indestructible. Bullets slide off you.\N{\rCHT}你這麼無堅不摧 子彈遇見你都會繞道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.52,1:24:21.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,You play with 'em.\N{\rCHT}這些對你來說都是小意思{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.66,1:24:25.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tony, I thought about my money.\N{\rCHT}托尼 我考慮了如何處理我的錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.90,1:24:35.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,You remember the girl who came here the other day?\N{\rCHT}你記得前幾天來這兒的女孩麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.66,1:24:36.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\rCHT}嗯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.53,1:24:43.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Her name is Mathilda.\N{\rCHT}她的名字是瑪蒂爾達{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.79,1:24:46.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,If anything happens to me...\N{\rCHT}如果我遭遇不測{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.84,1:24:54.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to give her...\N{\rCHT}我希望你能把我的錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.89,1:24:58.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,my money.\N{\rCHT}給她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.55,1:25:03.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can count on me, Leon.\N{\rCHT}這事包在我身上 里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.59,1:25:05.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tony.\N{\rCHT}謝謝你 托尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.51,1:25:11.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,I won't be long.\N{\rCHT}我很快就回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.73,1:25:15.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did I do something wrong?\N{\rCHT}我犯錯了嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.39,1:25:20.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,No. This one is too big.\N{\rCHT}沒有 這一單太大了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.69,1:25:24.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I only get the leftovers, is that it?\N{\rCHT}是啊 我只能挑你剩下的做 是這樣嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.79,1:25:30.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mathilda, since I met you everything's been different.\N{\rCHT}瑪蒂爾達 我遇見你之後 所有事情都不同了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.71,1:25:35.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I just need some time alone.\N{\rCHT}所以我就是想獨處一會兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.90,1:25:41.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,You need some time to grow up a little.\N{\rCHT}你需要一些時間成長{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.47,1:25:45.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,I finished growing up, Leon. I just get older.\N{\rCHT}我已經夠成熟了 里昂 我只會變老{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.55,1:25:48.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,For me it's the opposite. I'm old enough.\N{\rCHT}我正好相反 我已經夠老了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.83,1:25:52.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,I need time to grow up.\N{\rCHT}但我還不夠成熟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.90,1:26:08.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit.\N{\rCHT}媽的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.30,1:27:27.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on! Hustle!\N{\rCHT}快 投籃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.09,1:27:31.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Good shot. - Come on.\N{\rCHT}- 好球 - 過來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.58,1:27:37.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're new, aren't you? Fifth floor, right?\N{\rCHT}你剛搬過來對吧 住在五樓是嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.50,1:27:38.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can't sit here like that.\N{\rCHT}你不可以直接坐這兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.04,1:27:40.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Really, why not?\N{\rCHT}是嗎 為什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.25,1:27:42.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nothing's free. Like a parking meter.\N{\rCHT}這不是免費的 就像停車要收費{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.78,1:27:44.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,When you stop, you pay.\N{\rCHT}你停這兒 就要付錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.58,1:27:45.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's the law.\N{\rCHT}這是規矩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.90,1:27:47.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Only on T.V.\N{\rCHT}電視裡才這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.22,1:27:47.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you say?\N{\rCHT}你說什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.06,1:27:49.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Forget it. How much is your meter?\N{\rCHT}沒什麼 你要多少錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.22,1:27:52.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ten dollars a month.\N{\rCHT}十美元 每月{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.76,1:27:56.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Got change?\N{\rCHT}有錢找麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.26,1:28:01.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. We'll do ten for twelve.\N{\rCHT}算了 我一次性給你十個月的錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.42,1:28:03.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll pay now for the rest of the year.\N{\rCHT}就算我付了一年的錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.44,1:28:05.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, a year.\N{\rCHT}好的 一年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.38,1:28:07.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Does paying rent here mean\N{\rCHT}是不是我付了錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.62,1:28:11.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I have to put up with you guys? - Er, no.\N{\rCHT}- 還得忍受你們 - 額 不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.68,1:28:14.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,So go play somewhere else.\N{\rCHT}那就哪兒涼快哪兒呆著去吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.44,1:28:19.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,I need to think.\N{\rCHT}我需要思考{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.64,1:29:20.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stand up. Don't you like your job?\N{\rCHT}站直點 你是不是不想要你的工作了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.06,1:29:32.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Food.\N{\rCHT}吃的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.99,1:29:37.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where you going?\N{\rCHT}你去哪裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.76,1:29:40.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Special delivery, room 4602.\N{\rCHT}快遞 4602房間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.70,1:29:41.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sign here.\N{\rCHT}在這簽字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.37,1:29:49.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Have a nice weekend, girls.\N{\rCHT}週末愉快 姑娘們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.00,1:31:16.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Special delivery? Let me guess.\N{\rCHT}快遞是吧 讓我猜猜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.09,1:31:20.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Chinese?\N{\rCHT}中國菜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.72,1:31:25.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thai, maybe?\N{\rCHT}或者 泰國菜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.56,1:31:32.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've got it. Italian food.\N{\rCHT}我知道了 義大利菜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.45,1:31:51.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's your name, angel?\N{\rCHT}你叫什麼名字 寶貝兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.96,1:31:54.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mathilda.\N{\rCHT}瑪蒂爾達{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.08,1:31:56.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mathilda.\N{\rCHT}瑪蒂爾達{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.77,1:32:19.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mathilda.\N{\rCHT}瑪蒂爾達{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.11,1:32:24.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want you to put the sack on the floor.\N{\rCHT}把這袋東西放地上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.79,1:32:31.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good.\N{\rCHT}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.87,1:32:36.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now I want you to tell me\N{\rCHT}現在我希望你告訴我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.29,1:32:38.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,everything you know about Italian food.\N{\rCHT}你對"義大利菜"的瞭解{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.88,1:32:42.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the name of the chef who fixed it for me.\N{\rCHT}別忘了告訴我 那個讓你來的廚師的名字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.59,1:32:47.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nobody sent me. I do business for myself.\N{\rCHT}沒人叫我過來 是我自己要解決問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.81,1:32:55.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,So this is something personal, is it?\N{\rCHT}所以這是個人恩怨 對嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.19,1:33:05.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,What filthy piece of shit did I do now?\N{\rCHT}我他媽又做什麼了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.14,1:33:08.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,You killed my brother.\N{\rCHT}你殺了我弟弟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.44,1:33:14.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}對不起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.78,1:33:29.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,- And you wanna join him? - No.\N{\rCHT}- 你想和他一起嗎 - 不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.50,1:33:32.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's always the same thing.\N{\rCHT}人們都一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.50,1:33:41.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's when you start to become really afraid of death...\N{\rCHT}當你開始由衷地恐懼死亡時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.43,1:33:46.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,that you learn to appreciate life.\N{\rCHT}才開始學會珍惜生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.93,1:33:54.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Do you like life, sweetheart? - Yes.\N{\rCHT}- 你熱愛生活麼 寶貝 - 是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.07,1:34:00.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's good.\N{\rCHT}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.11,1:34:08.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because I take no pleasure\N{\rCHT}因為我不喜歡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.20,1:34:11.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,in taking a life\N{\rCHT}殺死一個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.46,1:34:16.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,if it's from a person who doesn't care about it.\N{\rCHT}不熱愛生命的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.97,1:34:27.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stan,\N{\rCHT}史丹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.93,1:34:29.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stan,\N{\rCHT}史丹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.89,1:34:32.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've been looking all over for you. I checked upstairs...\N{\rCHT}我剛剛到處找你 樓上找遍了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.82,1:34:34.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,What? I'm busy.\N{\rCHT}怎麼了 我現在很忙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.64,1:34:37.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's Malky, man. He's dead.\N{\rCHT}是瑪律奇 他死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.86,1:34:43.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Malky was makin' a buy for us from the Chinaman.\N{\rCHT}瑪律奇當時在中國人那裡幫我們買東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.19,1:34:45.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,But they got nothin' to do with it.\N{\rCHT}但他們與這件事無關{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.15,1:34:49.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,They told me this guy came from the outside.\N{\rCHT}他們告訴我殺手從外面進來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.20,1:34:55.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,He was a pro.He was fast. He fuckin' came out of nowhere.\N{\rCHT}是個職業殺手 動作麻利 不知道從哪裡冒出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.04,1:34:58.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Boom, shoots the Chinaman dead in two seconds.\N{\rCHT}砰 擊斃了那個中國人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.71,1:35:01.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Easy, man. I'm a cop.\N{\rCHT}別激動 我是員警{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.96,1:35:04.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then turns around, says something to Malky like...\N{\rCHT}然後他轉身 對瑪律奇說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.92,1:35:06.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,No women, no kids.\N{\rCHT}不殺女人和小孩兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.39,1:35:17.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think it was somethin' personal.\N{\rCHT}我覺得這是個人恩怨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.73,1:35:20.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Death is\N{\rCHT}今天的死神{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.36,1:35:23.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,whimsical today.\N{\rCHT}讓人捉摸不透{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.60,1:35:52.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Blood,\N{\rCHT}布拉德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.98,1:35:55.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,do you hear me?\N{\rCHT}你在聽我說嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.35,1:35:58.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I hear you, Stan. Just chill out, man.\N{\rCHT}是的 我聽著呢 史丹 別激動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.98,1:36:01.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Would you take her up to my office?\N{\rCHT}你能把她帶到我的辦公室嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.07,1:36:05.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, yeah.\N{\rCHT}可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.87,1:36:15.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus fucking Christ.\N{\rCHT}我滴個上帝啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.38,1:36:29.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Leon, my love.\N{\rCHT}"親愛的里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.01,1:36:32.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know where to find the guys who killed my brother.\N{\rCHT}我找到殺死我弟弟的人了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.43,1:36:33.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Their boss is Norman Stansfield.\N{\rCHT}他們的上司是諾曼·史丹菲爾德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.76,1:36:36.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's in the D.E.A. Building, room 4602.\N{\rCHT}他在聯邦大樓 4602號房間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.22,1:36:40.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna do them myself. If something goes wrong,\N{\rCHT}我要親手殺了他 如果我出了什麼意外{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.14,1:36:42.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,I left you 20 grand on the table.\N{\rCHT}我在桌上給你留了兩萬塊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.92,1:36:45.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's for a contract. Five grand a head, right?\N{\rCHT}合同規定好的 五千塊換一個人頭 對嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.19,1:36:49.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know I'll feel better after I do this.\N{\rCHT}只有殺了他我才能安心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.15,1:36:53.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,I love you. Mathilda.\N{\rCHT}我愛你 瑪蒂爾達{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.33,1:37:00.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wait for me. I won't be long.\N{\rCHT}在這兒等我 我去去就來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.12,1:37:03.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't park in front like this. It's a federal building!\N{\rCHT}我不能停在這裡 這是聯邦大樓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.71,1:37:10.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's gonna do the same exact thing that I said.\N{\rCHT}他會按我說的做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.93,1:37:12.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,A nine "Millie".\N{\rCHT}一把九釐米手槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.22,1:37:17.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bullets.Another nine "Millie".\N{\rCHT}子彈 又一把九釐米手槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.10,1:37:23.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,What'd you plan to do with all these guns?\N{\rCHT}你帶著這些槍是要幹嘛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.15,1:37:25.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Maybe she was planning on taking out the whole building.\N{\rCHT}她也許是想拿下整棟樓呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.40,1:37:33.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Holy shit! What we got here? Lunch.\N{\rCHT}天啊 看這是什麼 中飯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.53,1:37:38.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Careful, Blood, might be poisoned.\N{\rCHT}小心點 布拉德 可能有毒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.54,1:37:41.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,1991年 加州發生食用鯷魚 導致海鳥死亡的多莫酸中毒事件
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.54,1:37:41.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,No,man.There's no anchovies on this.\N{\rCHT}不會的 上面又沒有鯷魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.90,1:37:59.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is that what you call 'I won't be long'?\N{\rCHT}這就是你所謂的"去去就來"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.95,1:38:02.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,I been hanging around here for at least ten minutes.\N{\rCHT}我在這兒晃了至少有十分鐘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.91,1:38:03.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,I did my best.\N{\rCHT}我儘快了 走吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.62,1:38:54.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you like it?\N{\rCHT}你喜歡嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.71,1:38:56.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\rCHT}嗯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.63,1:38:58.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,So say it.\N{\rCHT}那就說出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.17,1:39:03.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,I like it.\N{\rCHT}我喜歡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.77,1:39:19.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not thirsty?\N{\rCHT}不渴嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.08,1:39:31.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, a girl's first time is very important.\N{\rCHT}你知道嗎 女孩的第一次非常重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.41,1:39:34.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,It determines the rest of her life sexually.\N{\rCHT}這決定了她之後的生活是否性福{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.50,1:39:37.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,I read that once in one of my sister's magazines.\N{\rCHT}我在姐姐的雜誌上看到的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.84,1:39:41.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,My girlfriends told me they hated their first experience.\N{\rCHT}我閨蜜告訴我 她們的第一次並不美好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.51,1:39:46.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's because they didn't love the guys.\N{\rCHT}因為她們不愛那些男的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.05,1:39:49.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,They just did it to show off.\N{\rCHT}她們那麼做只是為了以後炫耀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.30,1:39:53.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, they started liking it, like cigarettes.\N{\rCHT}但後來 她們開始享受了 感覺就像抽煙一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.04,1:40:00.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Will I like it the first time?\N{\rCHT}我的第一次會是美好的嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.66,1:40:06.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mathilda, no.\N{\rCHT}瑪蒂爾達 不行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.20,1:40:10.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why not?\N{\rCHT}為什麼不行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.15,1:40:12.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,I just can't.\N{\rCHT}我就是做不到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.21,1:40:15.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,You love someone else?\N{\rCHT}你愛著別人嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.00,1:40:18.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.I mean...\N{\rCHT}不 我的意思是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.28,1:40:25.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,There was someone a long time ago.\N{\rCHT}很久之前 在我還沒來美國的時候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.28,1:40:29.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Before I came to the States.\N{\rCHT}我愛過一個人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.01,1:40:32.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Her father didn't want her to see me.\N{\rCHT}她爸爸不希望她和我聯繫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.09,1:40:37.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,She was from a very respectable family.\N{\rCHT}她出身名門望族{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.78,1:40:40.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mine was...\N{\rCHT}而我家卻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.00,1:40:42.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,you know...\N{\rCHT}你懂的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.54,1:40:46.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,not so respectable.\N{\rCHT}沒什麼名望{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.67,1:40:50.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Her dad went nuts every time she'd take off to see me.\N{\rCHT}每次她出來見我 她爸爸就會抓狂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.84,1:40:52.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,She still snuck off to see you, right?\N{\rCHT}但她仍然偷偷溜出來見你 對吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.40,1:40:55.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Right.\N{\rCHT}對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.93,1:40:58.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,See, nothing can stop love, Leon.\N{\rCHT}你看 愛是不可阻擋的 里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.76,1:41:02.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,He killed her.\N{\rCHT}他殺了她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.32,1:41:05.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,One shot through the head.\N{\rCHT}對著她頭部開了一槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.02,1:41:13.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,They kept him in jail for two days, and they let him go free.\N{\rCHT}他只在監獄待了兩天 就被放出來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.21,1:41:16.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,They said it was an accident.\N{\rCHT}他們說那是場意外{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.53,1:41:20.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,So...\N{\rCHT}所以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.66,1:41:26.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,one night I waited for him.\N{\rCHT}有天晚上 我潛伏著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.54,1:41:30.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Five hundred feet with a lens.\N{\rCHT}在五百英尺外 用一支狙擊槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.84,1:41:35.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,He also had an accident.\N{\rCHT}也讓他發生了意外{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.11,1:41:40.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,The same night I took a boat and came here...\N{\rCHT}當天晚上 我坐船到了這裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.59,1:41:44.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,to meet up with my father who was working for Tony.\N{\rCHT}來投奔我的爸爸 他當時在為托尼工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.39,1:41:47.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was 19.\N{\rCHT}我那時十九歲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.81,1:41:55.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Since then I've never left the city, and...\N{\rCHT}從那以後 我就再沒離開過這座城市{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.23,1:42:00.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've never had another girlfriend.\N{\rCHT}也沒再談過戀愛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.00,1:42:05.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,You see, Mathilda...\N{\rCHT}你懂了吧 瑪蒂爾達{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.75,1:42:08.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be a good lover.\N{\rCHT}我不會是個好戀人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.99,1:42:12.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\rCHT}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.93,1:42:17.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Would you do me one favor?\N{\rCHT}你可以答應我一件事嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.24,1:42:19.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,What?\N{\rCHT}什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.92,1:42:22.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of watching you sleep on your chair.\N{\rCHT}我不想再看到你在椅子上睡覺了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.24,1:42:23.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're gonna share the bed.\N{\rCHT}我們同床睡吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.28,1:42:27.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's a good idea.\N{\rCHT}我覺得這樣不好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.08,1:42:32.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's okay.Put your legs up on the bed.\N{\rCHT}就這樣 把腿放到床上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.52,1:42:35.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's nice.\N{\rCHT}不錯 非常好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.79,1:42:41.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Put your head down. It's okay. Relax.\N{\rCHT}躺好 就這樣 放鬆點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.09,1:43:05.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good night, Leon.\N{\rCHT}晚安 里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.76,1:43:09.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good night.\N{\rCHT}晚安{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.44,1:43:46.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Manolo, take the kids in the kitchen.\N{\rCHT}馬諾洛 把孩子們帶進廚房{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.44,1:44:08.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of respect for your business, Tony.\N{\rCHT}我很尊重你的事業 托尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.80,1:44:12.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,When you've killed for us in the past...\N{\rCHT}你以前幫我們殺人的時候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.35,1:44:14.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,we've always been satisfied.\N{\rCHT}從沒讓我們失望過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.76,1:44:16.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why today\N{\rCHT}正因為如此{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.83,1:44:20.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,is going to be very hard for me.\N{\rCHT}今天我非常為難{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.72,1:44:22.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll excuse my mood.\N{\rCHT}希望你能體諒我的情緒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.87,1:44:30.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,My man was killed right here on your turf.\N{\rCHT}我的人就在你的地盤上被殺了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.29,1:44:34.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Chinks tell me that the hit man...\N{\rCHT}中國佬告訴我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.07,1:44:37.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,was kind of the Italian type.\N{\rCHT}殺手有點像義大利人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.22,1:44:41.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,So we figured that Tony might know something.\N{\rCHT}所以我們想 托尼也許知道些什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.01,1:44:42.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wait.\N{\rCHT}等等{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.51,1:44:46.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's more.You're gonna love this.\N{\rCHT}聽我說完 還有更精彩的呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.89,1:44:53.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,A few hours later, a little 12-year-old girl\N{\rCHT}幾小時之後 一個十二歲的小女孩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.11,1:44:55.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,comes into my office armed to the teeth,\N{\rCHT}全副武裝地 闖進我辦公的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.71,1:44:56.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,with the firm intention\N{\rCHT}鐵了心地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.69,1:44:58.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,of sending me straight to the morgue.\N{\rCHT}要把我送進太平間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.07,1:45:02.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you know who came and got her in the middle of the afternnon right there\N{\rCHT}你知道下午從我的地盤上把她救出去的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.15,1:45:03.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,in my building?\N{\rCHT}是誰嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.87,1:45:08.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,The very same Italian hit man.\N{\rCHT}就是那個義大利殺手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.29,1:45:15.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm dying to meet him.\N{\rCHT}我特別想會一會他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.18,1:45:22.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Relax. Everything's fine.\N{\rCHT}別緊張 一切正常{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.76,1:45:24.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sleep well?\N{\rCHT}睡得好嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.76,1:45:26.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,I never really sleep.\N{\rCHT}我從沒真正睡著過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.95,1:45:28.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Got one eye open always.\N{\rCHT}一直不敢睡得太熟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.89,1:45:29.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I forgot.\N{\rCHT}是哦 我忘了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.06,1:45:32.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,I never saw someone\N{\rCHT}我可從沒見過誰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.23,1:45:34.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,with one eye open snore so much.\N{\rCHT}睡得不熟 呼嚕還能打得這麼響{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.73,1:45:36.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I snore?\N{\rCHT}我打呼了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.44,1:45:37.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Like a baby.\N{\rCHT}像個嬰兒一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.11,1:45:42.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get some milk for breakfast. I won't be long.\N{\rCHT}我去買些牛奶當早餐 很快就回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.07,1:45:44.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the code when you come back.\N{\rCHT}回來時別忘了暗號{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.12,1:45:47.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Two knocks, then one, and two knocks again. Right?\N{\rCHT}兩下 一下 然後再兩下 對吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.83,1:45:48.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Right.\N{\rCHT}對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.76,1:46:11.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello, Signore. Ring these up. I'm gonna go get some milk.\N{\rCHT}先生您好 算算這些多少錢 我去拿點牛奶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.83,1:46:34.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,From here on out, you don't make a sound.\N{\rCHT}從現在起不許出聲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.83,1:46:36.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,You answer my questions by nodding yes\N{\rCHT}你需要回答我的問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.50,1:46:38.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,or shaking your head no. You got it?\N{\rCHT}點頭肯定 搖頭否定 明白了嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.30,1:46:40.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is he alone?\N{\rCHT}他只有一個人嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.49,1:46:42.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Does he expect you?\N{\rCHT}他在等你嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.68,1:46:45.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you have keys to the apartment?\N{\rCHT}你有房間的鑰匙嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.93,1:46:49.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is there a code, a way of knocking, so he knows it's you?\N{\rCHT}你們之間有識別身份的敲門暗號嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.56,1:47:39.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Alpha team.\N{\rCHT}阿爾法隊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.73,1:47:41.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Final position. We're ready to go.\N{\rCHT}已就位 準備就緒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.28,1:47:43.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Be careful.\N{\rCHT}小心點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.16,1:48:32.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Move! Move!\N{\rCHT}退後 退後{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.17,1:48:40.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit.\N{\rCHT}該死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.25,1:48:44.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Alpha team. Man down. Man down.\N{\rCHT}阿爾法隊 人員傷亡 人員傷亡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.55,1:48:46.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,I told you.\N{\rCHT}我提醒過你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.76,1:48:49.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Benny.\N{\rCHT}本尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.51,1:48:52.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bring me everyone.\N{\rCHT}把所有人都找來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.47,1:48:54.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "Everyone"?\N{\rCHT}所有人是什麼意思{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.39,1:48:57.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Everyone!\N{\rCHT}每 一 個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.61,1:49:51.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take this.\N{\rCHT}拿著這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.41,1:49:59.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go take a look.\N{\rCHT}去看一眼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.85,1:50:17.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't move.\N{\rCHT}別動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.85,1:50:19.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you see anything?\N{\rCHT}你看見什麼了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.68,1:50:21.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's the guy.\N{\rCHT}是他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.10,1:50:24.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's here. He's got a gun to my head.\N{\rCHT}他就在這兒 拿槍指著我的頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.02,1:50:29.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ok. Nobody moves.\N{\rCHT}知道了 大家都別動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.69,1:50:30.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let the girl go.\N{\rCHT}把那女孩放了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.57,1:50:33.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, man!\N{\rCHT}兄弟 冷靜點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.32,1:50:35.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let the girl go.\N{\rCHT}把那女孩放了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.03,1:50:36.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, the girl's comin' out.\N{\rCHT}好的 我們放她走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.49,1:50:38.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let the girl go.\N{\rCHT}把這女孩放了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.21,1:50:51.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Grab the axe off the wall. Over there. Go!\N{\rCHT}把斧子從牆上取下來 在那兒 快去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.89,1:50:56.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're coming with us.\N{\rCHT}你得跟我們走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.57,1:51:10.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Christ, he shot him!\N{\rCHT}天哪 他沖他開槍了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.81,1:51:13.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bastard!\N{\rCHT}混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.79,1:51:26.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Move! Move! Move! Move!\N{\rCHT}閃 閃 閃 閃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.46,1:51:30.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shut the fucking water off!\N{\rCHT}去把這該死的水關了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.77,1:51:31.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Got it.\N{\rCHT}明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.45,1:51:32.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come\N{\rCHT}過來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.99,1:51:36.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're in a bad way here.\N{\rCHT}我們處於劣勢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.15,1:51:38.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Send the cats.I repeat,sent the cats.\N{\rCHT}派人進來 再說一遍 派人進來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.52,1:51:49.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened.\N{\rCHT}我不知道是怎麼回事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.72,1:51:52.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,I didn't see 'em coming, I swear!\N{\rCHT}我沒看到他們進來 我發誓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.40,1:51:55.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,I just went shopping\N{\rCHT}我只是去買東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.86,1:51:57.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I came back, and they were everywhere.\N{\rCHT}回來的時候 他們就把樓封鎖了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.37,1:52:01.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stay away from the window.\N{\rCHT}不要靠近窗戶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.81,1:52:31.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leon.\N{\rCHT}里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.98,1:52:33.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leon.\N{\rCHT}里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.12,1:52:49.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come here.\N{\rCHT}過來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.54,1:52:53.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Snipers.\N{\rCHT}是狙擊手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.51,1:52:59.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, now, get this fucking asshole out of there.\N{\rCHT}現在 把那個混蛋給我抓出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.90,1:53:19.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,How are we gonna get outta here now?\N{\rCHT}我們要怎麼出去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.74,1:53:21.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me. We're checking out.\N{\rCHT}交給我吧 是時候退房了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.72,1:54:23.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,But Leon it's not big enough for you.\N{\rCHT}但是里昂 這兒對你來說太窄了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.26,1:54:25.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's barely big enough for me.\N{\rCHT}只能勉強夠我鑽進去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.60,1:54:26.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,We said no discussion.\N{\rCHT}說好了都聽我的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.93,1:54:28.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not letting...\N{\rCHT}不 我不會拋下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.11,1:54:32.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not going! I won't go!\N{\rCHT}我不走 我絕對不走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.60,1:54:35.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.\N{\rCHT}聽我說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.48,1:54:36.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have no chance together.\N{\rCHT}我們一起的話 沒有逃生的可能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.83,1:54:38.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,But if I'm alone, I can do it.\N{\rCHT}但如果我單獨行動 就能逃掉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.49,1:54:40.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Trust me. I'm in good shape, Mathilda.\N{\rCHT}相信我 我很強的 瑪蒂爾達{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.77,1:54:43.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know I've got a lot of money with Tony, a lot.\N{\rCHT}我在托尼那兒存了一大筆錢 一大筆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.44,1:54:44.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll take it and leave together,\N{\rCHT}我們帶上那筆錢一起遠走高飛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.78,1:54:46.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,just the two of us.Okay? Go.\N{\rCHT}就我們兩個人 好嗎 快走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.88,1:54:51.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,No! You're saying that so I won't worry.\N{\rCHT}不要 你只是在安慰我而已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.24,1:54:56.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna lose you, Leon.\N{\rCHT}我不想失去你 里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.91,1:54:58.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna lose me, Mathilda.\N{\rCHT}你不會失去我的 瑪蒂爾達{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.66,1:55:00.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,You've given me a taste for life.\N{\rCHT}你讓我體會到生命的真諦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.58,1:55:03.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wanna be happy, sleep in a bed, have roots.\N{\rCHT}我想要做快樂的人 睡在床上 落地生根{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.04,1:55:06.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,You'll never be alone again.\N{\rCHT}我不會再讓你孤身一人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.55,1:55:12.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please, go now, baby. Go.\N{\rCHT}求你了 快走吧 寶貝兒 快走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.59,1:55:17.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Go now. Go.\N{\rCHT}冷靜點 快離開這兒 去吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.77,1:55:22.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,See you at Tony's. I'm gonna clean them all.\N{\rCHT}我們在托尼那兒見 我會把他們全部殺掉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.60,1:55:24.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tony's in an hour.\N{\rCHT}一小時後托尼那兒見{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.15,1:55:32.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,I love you, Mathilda.\N{\rCHT}我愛你 瑪蒂爾達{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.07,1:55:34.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,I love you, too, Leon.\N{\rCHT}我也愛你 里昂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.02,1:56:11.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the fuck is going on up there?\N{\rCHT}喂 樓上他媽的在幹什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.61,1:56:15.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,I just said "Take the guy out", not the fucking building.\N{\rCHT}我只說要抓住那個男的 不是讓你們拆了這棟操蛋的樓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.76,1:56:37.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,We've got one breathing here!\N{\rCHT}這兒還有一個活人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.76,1:56:41.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get a medic on the horn!\N{\rCHT}快叫醫生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.31,1:56:51.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,We've got a wounded man. Make way!\N{\rCHT}這裡有一個傷患 讓一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.82,1:56:53.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Down those stairs.\N{\rCHT}把他送下樓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.90,1:56:57.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Move!\N{\rCHT}下來 快點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.28,1:57:00.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get that guy off the stairs! Lay him on the layer.\N{\rCHT}把傷患送下樓 放在擔架上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.53,1:57:02.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get your team back out there!\N{\rCHT}讓你的人退到那兒去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.58,1:57:06.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,We've got two men comin' down the stairs. Let's hurry!\N{\rCHT}有兩名隊員要下樓 抓緊時間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.16,1:57:32.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,You okay? Hey, I need a medic over here!\N{\rCHT}你還好嗎 嘿 這裡需要一個醫生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:32.68,1:57:34.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Move your fuckin' asses.\N{\rCHT}快滾過去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.36,1:57:36.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Squad Number One, what's the status on the apartment?\N{\rCHT}第一小隊 房間裡現在是什麼情況{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.86,1:57:38.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can't see shit. Too much smoke.\N{\rCHT}煙太濃了 屁都看不見{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.09,1:57:39.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Give us five minutes.\N{\rCHT}再給我們五分鐘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.58,1:57:40.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay. You got it.\N{\rCHT}好的 去吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.65,1:57:42.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,What? Two hundred men\N{\rCHT}什麼 兩百個大漢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.49,1:57:46.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,can't find one man and a girl? Did you find the girl?\N{\rCHT}還找不到一個男人和一個小女孩嗎 找到小女孩了嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.67,1:57:58.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hi, how are you doing? Take your mask off, quick.\N{\rCHT}嗨 感覺怎麼樣 把你的面罩摘下來 快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.97,1:58:05.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let me see you. That's deep. Right. And this one here...\N{\rCHT}讓我檢查一下你的傷口 很深啊 好 再檢查一下這裡的傷口{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.21,1:58:06.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're from the 3rd Precinct?\N{\rCHT}你是第三警區來的嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.61,1:58:12.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's open up his sleeve a little bit.\N{\rCHT}來把他的袖子稍微弄開一點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.05,1:58:20.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, fine. Put it down. This one.\N{\rCHT}沒事了 放下吧 換這只手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.09,1:58:39.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,You stay there for two minutes. I'll be right back.\N{\rCHT}在這兒等兩分鐘 我馬上回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:39.22,1:58:42.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let me put the mask back on. I breathe better with it.\N{\rCHT}讓我把面罩帶上 這樣呼吸更順暢一點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.30,1:58:45.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,OK. You're all right. Sit tight.\N{\rCHT}好的 你不會有事的 坐著別動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.81,1:58:54.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, everybody out!\N{\rCHT}快點 所有人都出去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.90,1:58:57.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Out!\N{\rCHT}走走走 都出去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.22,1:59:24.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Clear the way, men.\N{\rCHT}哥們 給他讓條道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.48,1:59:37.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here? Get out. Come on.\N{\rCHT}你在這兒幹什麼呢 趕緊離開 快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.55,2:01:30.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stansfield?\N{\rCHT}史丹菲爾德嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.01,2:01:32.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,At your service.\N{\rCHT}靜候差遣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.48,2:01:44.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is from...\N{\rCHT}這個是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.28,2:01:52.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mathilda.\N{\rCHT}替瑪蒂爾達給的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:09.47,2:02:10.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit.\N{\rCHT}媽的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.16,2:02:40.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leon asked me to help you out if somethin' happened,\N{\rCHT}里昂說 如果出事了就讓我幫你一把{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.46,2:02:44.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I think somethin' happened, right?\N{\rCHT}我想應該是出事了 對吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:44.63,2:02:47.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,He put aside a little cash for you.\N{\rCHT}他為你留了點錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:47.46,2:02:50.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,So what I'm suggesting is that...\N{\rCHT}我是這麼想的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.68,2:02:53.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,seein' as how you're still so young...\N{\rCHT}你還這麼年輕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.26,2:02:56.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,I should hold the money for you until you're older.\N{\rCHT}所以在你長大之前 就由我來替你保管這筆錢吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:56.35,2:02:58.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Like a bank, you know, except...\N{\rCHT}你懂的 就像銀行一樣 只不過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:58.39,2:03:01.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,it's better than a bank 'cause banks always get knocked off.\N{\rCHT}我這兒比銀行更保險 因為銀行總會破產{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:02.73,2:03:04.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,No one knocks off old Tony.\N{\rCHT}而老托尼始終屹立不倒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:04.86,2:03:07.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,But it's your money. In the meantime...\N{\rCHT}不過這畢竟是你的錢 在這期間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:08.23,2:03:12.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,all you gotta do is come here every once in a while...\N{\rCHT}你只需要隔三差五來這兒一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:12.43,2:03:15.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I'll dish it out so you can have a little fun, OK?\N{\rCHT}從我這兒取點錢去找樂子 好嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.70,2:03:21.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here's a hundred bucks to start.\N{\rCHT}開始就先給你一百塊吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:22.37,2:03:24.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can't I get a job instead?\N{\rCHT}我不能在這兒工作嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.63,2:03:25.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,A job?\N{\rCHT}你說工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.84,2:03:29.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the hell can you do?\N{\rCHT}你又能做些什麼鬼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:29.34,2:03:31.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can clean.\N{\rCHT}我會殺人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.18,2:03:34.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,I ain't got no work for a 12-year-old kid...\N{\rCHT}我這兒可沒有能讓十二歲小孩做的工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.94,2:03:37.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,so get it out of your goddamn head!\N{\rCHT}別再有這樣該死的想法了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:37.43,2:03:41.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's over! The game's over!Leon's dead!\N{\rCHT}都結束了 遊戲結束了 里昂死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.15,2:03:43.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,You hear me?\N{\rCHT}聽懂了沒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.01,2:03:56.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on. You think I ain't hurtin' too?\N{\rCHT}好了 你覺得我就不難過嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:01.85,2:04:03.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,But he's dead.\N{\rCHT}但是他已經死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.49,2:04:06.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're gonna forget all this craziness\N{\rCHT}你得把這些破事兒都忘了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:06.71,2:04:09.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,and get your little ass back to school, capito?\N{\rCHT}然後好好滾回學校念書 懂了嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.88,2:04:12.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now take this money and get the hell outta here.\N{\rCHT}現在拿上這些錢 快滾吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:12.88,2:04:15.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't let me see your face till next month...\N{\rCHT}這個月內別讓我再看到你的臉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.05,2:04:16.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,'cause something tells me\N{\rCHT}因為我感覺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.43,2:04:18.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm about to lose my famous kind streak.\N{\rCHT}我一直以來的好脾氣就快崩不住了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.81,2:05:12.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,My parents...\N{\rCHT}我的父母{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.49,2:05:19.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,died in a car accident four weeks ago.\N{\rCHT}四周前在車禍中喪生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:21.33,2:05:22.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,It was terrible.\N{\rCHT}那太可怕了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:25.48,2:05:27.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,We didn't have the time\N{\rCHT}在你第一次來這兒的時候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.37,2:05:29.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,to get to know one another when you first came here...\N{\rCHT}我們沒有時間互相瞭解{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:29.40,2:05:31.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,but I want you to know\N{\rCHT}但我希望你能明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.63,2:05:34.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not the kind of woman who'd let down a child...\N{\rCHT}我絕不會讓一個孩子感到失望{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:34.13,2:05:36.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,whatever her situation, whatever her mistake.\N{\rCHT}不管她的處境如何 也不管她犯了什麼錯誤{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:37.08,2:05:39.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to help you\N{\rCHT}所以我會幫助你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:39.07,2:05:42.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,and do my best to welcome you here again.\N{\rCHT}也真心實意地歡迎你回到這裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:44.52,2:05:46.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,But on one condition:\N{\rCHT}但是我有一個條件{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:46.84,2:05:49.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,You have to stop lying to me, Mathilda.\N{\rCHT}你必須告訴我實話 瑪蒂爾達{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.52,2:05:54.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want you to take a chance and trust me.\N{\rCHT}我希望你能試著相信我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.26,2:05:57.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now tell me what happened to you.\N{\rCHT}現在告訴我到底發生了什麼事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.07,2:06:00.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\rCHT}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.71,2:06:04.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,My family got shot down by D.E.A. Officers...\N{\rCHT}我的家人因為毒品糾紛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:04.95,2:06:06.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,because of a drug problem.\N{\rCHT}被緝毒組的員警開槍打死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.50,2:06:10.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,I left with the greatest guy on Earth.\N{\rCHT}一個世界上最好的男人帶我逃走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:11.12,2:06:13.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,He was a hit man, the best in town,\N{\rCHT}他是一個職業殺手 在鎮上首屈一指{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:14.36,2:06:15.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,but he died this morning.\N{\rCHT}但是今天早上他死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:15.88,2:06:17.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you don't help me,\N{\rCHT}如果你不幫我的話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:17.70,2:06:19.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll be dead by tonight.\N{\rCHT}可能我今晚就會死掉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.32,2:06:40.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know her?\N{\rCHT}你們認識她嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:42.03,2:06:43.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've never seen her.\N{\rCHT}從來沒見過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:09.21,2:07:11.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think we'll be okay here.Leon.\N{\rCHT}我想我們能在這兒安心生活了 里昂{\r}
