Dialogue: 0,2:07:13.45,2:07:24.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,∮He deals the cards as a meditation And those he plays never suspect∮\N{\rCHT}他玩牌的樣子似在冥想 從未有人懷疑他的智商{\r}
