Dialogue: 0,2:07:36.30,2:07:46.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,∮He deals the cards to find the answer The sacred geometry of chance∮\N{\rCHT}他只想找到一個答案 那神秘的幾何概率{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.44,2:07:56.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,∮The hidden law of a probable outcome The numbers lead a dance∮\N{\rCHT}那無法預料的結果 各種法則在數字下隱藏{\r}
